NK113(e)002:1: // tsan+d+ra pra d+ai pa n+aa ma gu na ra t+na
NK113(e)002:2: ko sha s+ya bri t+ti dwi sa t+yam b+h+aa s+k+aa
NK113(e)002:3: ra bi ha ra ti sma ////
NK113(e)002:4: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod kyi 'grel pa bden
NK113(e)002:5: gnyis gsal byed zla ba'i sgron me zhes bya ba
NK113(e)002:6: bzhugs so // na mahdz+ny+aa na sat+wa ye /
NK113(e)002:7: don gyi dam pa rnam dag dpal //
NK113(e)002:8: 'jig rten gsum na skal bzang che //
NK113(e)002:9: smon lam ye shes rgya mtsho ste //
NK113(e)002:11: gang gi mkhyen brtse'i rnam rol ni //
NK113(e)002:12: gdul bya'i dpal du yongs shar ba //
NK113(e)002:13: snga 'gyur bstan pa'i sgron me mchog /
NK113(e)002:15: de yi thugs mdzod las byung ba'i //
NK113(e)002:16: theg dgu'i don bcud bsdus pa'i gzhung //
NK113(e)002:17: blo dman rnams la phan pa'i blos //
NK113(e)002:18: rang nus ji bzhin 'dir gsal bya //
NK113(e)002:19: de la 'dir rgyal ba thabs mkhas la thugs rje
NK113(e)002:20: chen po dang ldan pa nyid kyi gdul bya'i khams
NK113(e)002:21: dbang mos pa dang 'tshams pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs
NK113(e)002:22: bsam gyis mi khyab pa zhig gsungs pa thams cad
NK113(e)002:23: kyi don bsdu na mdo sngags gnyis sam skyes bu
NK113(e)002:24: gsum gyi lam gyi rim par 'du la /
NK113(e)002:25: de lta bu'i chos thams cad gzhung lam gcig tu
NK113(e)002:26: ston pa'i bstan bcos yon tan rin po che'i mdzod
NK113(e)002:27: 'di 'chad par byed pa la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:28: bshad bya'i yan lag bshad pa dang /
NK113(e)002:30: dang po bshad bya'i yan lag bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK113(e)002:31: slob dpon gyis chos ji ltar 'chad tshul /
NK113(e)002:32: slob mas ji ltar nyan tshul /
NK113(e)002:33: de gnyis kas 'chad nyan ji ltar bgyi ba'i tshul lo //
NK113(e)002:34: dang po slob dpon gyis chos ji ltar 'chad tshul la gsum ste /
NK113(e)002:35: slob dpon sangs rgyas kyis chos ji ltar 'chad tshul /
NK113(e)002:36: slob dpon dgra bcom pas chos ji ltar 'chad tshul /
NK113(e)002:37: slob dpon mkhas pa pan+di tas chos ji ltar 'chad tshul lo //
NK113(e)002:38: dang po slob dpon sangs rgyas kyis cho 'phrul gsum la brten nas 'chad de /
NK113(e)002:39: de yang sku rdzu 'phrul gyi cho 'phrul smin mtshams
NK113(e)002:40: kyi mdzod spu nas 'od zer spro ba sogs kyis
NK113(e)002:41: gdul bya 'khor du ma 'dus pa bsdus nas ljags
NK113(e)002:42: kyi dbang pos stong gsum khebs par mdzad pa sogs
NK113(e)002:43: kyiis gdul bya 'khor du 'dus pa rnams yid ches
NK113(e)002:44: par mdzad / thugs kun tu brjod pa'i cho 'phrul
NK113(e)002:45: gyis gdul bya 'khor du 'dus pa de dag gi
NK113(e)002:46: blo dang dbang po bag la nyal ba thams cad
NK113(e)002:48: gsung rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul gyis 'gro ba
NK113(e)002:49: rang rang gi skad dang mthun pa'i gsung tshangs dbyangs
NK113(e)002:50: yan lag drug cu dang ldan pa'i sgo nas gang
NK113(e)002:51: la gang gis 'dul ba'i chos de dang de 'chad
NK113(e)002:52: ba'o // gnyis pa slob dpon dgra bcom pas dag pa gsum la brten nas 'chad de /
NK113(e)002:53: nyan pa po'i snod dag pa gzhan sems shes pa'i
NK113(e)002:54: mngon shes kyis gdul bya de'i rgyud brtags nas rgyud
NK113(e)002:55: snod rung du gyur na chos 'chad /
NK113(e)002:56: 'chad pa po'i ngag dag pa chags sogs nyon mongs
NK113(e)002:57: pa'i sgrib pa las grol ba'i ngag tshig dri ma
NK113(e)002:58: med pa brda' dag snyan pa'i dbyangs kyis 'chad /
NK113(e)002:59: gsung rab kyi brjod bya dag pa rang nyid kyi
NK113(e)002:60: yongs 'dzin rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas la sogs pa'i zhal
NK113(e)002:61: nas ji ltar gsungs pa ltar mi brjed pa'i gzungs
NK113(e)002:62: kyis bzung ste tshig la lhag chad dang don la
NK113(e)002:64: 'o na nyan thos dgra bcom pa de dag gis
NK113(e)002:65: cho 'phrul rnam pa gsum la brten nas ci'i phyir
NK113(e)002:67: de dag la mi shes pa'i rgyu bzhi yod pas
NK113(e)002:68: cho 'phrul gsum la brten nas 'chad mi nus te
NK113(e)002:69: / gnas kyis bskal pas mi shes pa 'phags pa
NK113(e)002:70: mo'u gal gyi bu chen pos rang gi ma sangs
NK113(e)002:71: rgyas kyi zhing 'od zer can du skyes pa ma
NK113(e)002:73: dus kyis bskal pas mi shes pa khyim bdag dpal
NK113(e)002:74: skyes kyi rgyud la thar pa'i sa bon yod pa
NK113(e)002:75: 'phags pa sh+aa ri'i bus ma shes pa lta bu
NK113(e)002:76: / rgyu thug med kyi 'bras bu thug med mi shes pa /
NK113(e)002:78: rma bya'i mdongs bkra gcig la yang /
NK113(e)002:79: rgyu yi dbye ba tha dad pa //
NK113(e)002:80: de mkhyen pa ni kun mkhyen te //
NK113(e)002:81: kun mkhyen ye shes min pas min //
NK113(e)002:83: sangs rgyas kyi chos rab tu mang po mi shes te /
NK113(e)002:85: ma 'dres pa la sogs pa med pa'o //
NK113(e)002:86: gsum pa slob dpon mkhas pa pan+di tas chos ji ltar 'chad tshul la gnyis /
NK113(e)002:87: chos kyi 'byung gnas rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul na
NK113(e)002:88: gtsug lag khang chen po gnyis yod pa'i dpal na
NK113(e)002:89: len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang na bzhugs pa'i pan+di ta rnams
NK113(e)002:90: kyis ni / bka' thams cad phun sum tshogs pa
NK113(e)002:91: lnga dang bstan bcos thams cad rtsis mgo yan lag
NK113(e)002:93: bi kra ma sh+r+ai la'i gtsug lag khang na bzhugs
NK113(e)002:94: pa'i pan+di ta rnams kyis nyan pa po snod rung
NK113(e)002:96: bstan pa'i rnam bzhag nges pa gnyis kyi sgo nas 'chad //
NK113(e)002:97: de gnyis las 'dir snga ma'i rjes su 'brang nas 'chad de /
NK113(e)002:98: skabs 'dir bstan bcos yon tan rin po che'i mdzod
NK113(e)002:99: 'di nyid rtsis mgo yan lag lnga'i sgo nas 'chad
NK113(e)002:100: pa la / mdzad pa po sus mdzad /
NK113(e)002:103: dbu nas zhabs su bsdus pa'i don gang yin //
NK113(e)002:104: dgos ched su zhig gi don du mdzad ce na /
NK113(e)002:105: dang po mdzad pa po ni /
NK113(e)002:106: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i gnas lugs bya rtsol
NK113(e)002:107: dang bral ba'i klong du chos nyid kyi bden pa
NK113(e)002:108: mngon sum du gzigs pas dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab
NK113(e)002:109: bdag rdo rje 'chang dang gnyis med du bzhugs shing
NK113(e)002:110: / rig rtsal so sor rtog pa'i ye shes su
NK113(e)002:111: 'bar bas rig pa'i gnas chen lnga sogs shes bya'i
NK113(e)002:112: chos thams cad ma bslab par mkhyen pa'i klong rdol
NK113(e)002:113: te bstan bcos rtsom pa'i rgyu gsum legs par tshang
NK113(e)002:114: / zhing / khyad par mchims phu nags kyi dur
NK113(e)002:115: khrod du lo gsum snying po'i sgrub pa la gzhol
NK113(e)002:116: / zhing / ba'i tshe / kun mkhyen chos kyi
NK113(e)002:117: rgyal po dri med 'od zer dpal ngag gi dbang
NK113(e)002:118: phyug gis ye shes kyi sku'i rjes su bzung nas
NK113(e)002:119: sku gsung thugs kyi byin gyis brlabs te dgongs pa
NK113(e)002:120: dbyer med du gyur nas bstan pa'i mnga' bdag chen
NK113(e)002:121: por bzhugs pa rig 'dzin 'jigs med gling pa'am pad+ma
NK113(e)002:122: dbang chen ye shes rol pa'i rdo rjes mdzad //
NK113(e)002:123: lung gang nas btus na sangs rgyas kyi chos gsung
NK113(e)002:124: rab sde snod gsum rgyud sde bzhi dgongs 'grel dang
NK113(e)002:126: phyogs gang du gtogs na spyir theg pa che chung gnyis las chen po'i phyogs su gtogs /
NK113(e)002:127: theg chen mdo sngags gnyis las sngags phyogs /
NK113(e)002:128: gsang sngags phyi nang gnyis las nang rgyud bla na med pa'i phyogs su gtso bor gtogs so //
NK113(e)002:129: dbu nas zhabs su bsdus pa'i don gang yin zhe na /
NK113(e)002:130: skyes bu gsum gyi lam gyi rim pa thams cad
NK113(e)002:131: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam stegs su bkral
NK113(e)002:132: te blo rab 'bring tha gsum mthar thug gi lam
NK113(e)002:133: du skyel so mthun par byas pa'o //
NK113(e)002:134: dgos ched su zhig gi don du mdzad ce na /
NK113(e)002:135: sngar bshad pa ltar kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal po'i
NK113(e)002:136: zhal mjal ba'i tshe dpe cha bam po zhig gtad
NK113(e)002:137: de 'dir shing rta chen po na gab pa'i tshul
NK113(e)002:138: du yod pa thams cad gsal por yod pa yin
NK113(e)002:139: zhes bstan bcos rtsom pa'i gnang ba byin pa bzhin
NK113(e)002:140: shing rta chen por rgyal par ma bkral ba'i so
NK113(e)002:141: thar dang sngags thun mong ba'i skor rnams rtsal du
NK113(e)002:143: phyi rabs rjes 'jug gi gang zag rnams kyis bstan pa thams cad 'gal med du rtogs pa dang /
NK113(e)002:144: rgyal ba'i gzhung lam tshang la ma nor ba gang
NK113(e)002:145: zag gcig 'tshang rgya ba'i lam du bsdus nas nyams
NK113(e)002:146: su len shes pa'i don du mdzad pa sde /
NK113(e)002:147: de ltar rtsis mgo yan lag lngas gtan la phabs
NK113(e)002:148: pas nyan pa pos yid ches thob nas chos kyi
NK113(e)002:149: snod rung du 'gyur pa'i dgos pa yod pa'o //
NK113(e)002:150: gnyis pa slob mas ji ltar nyan pa'i tshul la kun slong dang kun spyod gnyis /
NK113(e)002:151: dang po kun slong bsam pa bzang po byang chub kyi sems kyis zin par bya ba ste /
NK113(e)002:152: 'di ltar 'khor ba na gnas sems can thams cad
NK113(e)002:153: thog ma med pa'i dus nas pha mar ma gyur
NK113(e)002:154: pa med la pha mar gyur pa'i dus su da
NK113(e)002:155: lta'i pha ma bzhin du drin chen pos bskyangs te
NK113(e)002:158: shin tu byams pas bskyed bsrings pa'i drin can sha stag yin la /
NK113(e)002:159: drin can de dag thams cad 'dod pa bde ba
NK113(e)002:160: 'dod kyang bde ba'i rgyu chos dge ba la spyod
NK113(e)002:161: mi shes par sdug bsngal gyi rgyu mi dge ba
NK113(e)002:162: kho na dang du blangs te zhe 'dod dang lag
NK113(e)002:163: len phyin ci log tu gyur nas lam log mgo
NK113(e)002:164: rmongs su gyur / long ba thang dkyil du lus
NK113(e)002:165: pa lta bu'i sems can 'di rnams snying re rje
NK113(e)002:166: rmongs su gyur / / bdag da res dal 'byor gyi mi lus thob /
NK113(e)002:167: mtshan ldan gyi bla ma mjal /
NK113(e)002:168: yang dag pa'i chos la spyod du yod pa 'di
NK113(e)002:169: skal ba bzang bas le lo dang phyi bshol gyi
NK113(e)002:171: dam pa'i chos zab mo 'di lta bu nyan nas
NK113(e)002:172: nyams su blangs te ma rgan sems can thams cad
NK113(e)002:173: rigs drug so so'i las snang sdug bsngal bag chags
NK113(e)002:174: thams cad dang bral nas rnam mkhyen rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK113(e)002:175: rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya'i snyam du sems
NK113(e)002:176: bskyed pa ni gal che ba'i gnad dam pa'o //
NK113(e)002:177: gnyis pa kun spyod la spang bya'i kun spyod dang blang bya'i kun spyod gnyis /
NK113(e)002:178: dang po spang bya'i kun spyod la /
NK113(e)002:181: mi 'dzin pa lnga dang bcas pa spang dgos te /
NK113(e)002:182: dang po snod kyi skyon gsum ni /
NK113(e)002:183: rna ba mi gtad kha sbub lta bu'i skyon //
NK113(e)002:184: yid la mi 'dzin zhabs rdol lta bu'i skyon //
NK113(e)002:185: nyon mongs dang 'dres dug can lta bu'i skyon //
NK113(e)002:189: nga rgyal dang ni ma dad dang //
NK113(e)002:190: don du gnyer ba med nyid dang //
NK113(e)002:191: phyi rol rnam g.yeng nang du sdud //
NK113(e)002:192: skyo bas nyan pa dri ma yin //
NK113(e)002:193: zhes pa ltar chos 'chad pa po'i bla ma las kyang nga mkhas snyam pa'i nga rgyal /
NK113(e)002:194: chos dang bla ma'i skyon la rtog pa'i ma dad pa /
NK113(e)002:195: chos thob kyang rung ma thob kyang rung snyam pa'i don gnyer med pa /
NK113(e)002:196: sems phyi rol tshogs drug gi yul la g.yengs pa /
NK113(e)002:197: sems ha cang nang du sdud ches pas gnyid dang rmugs par 'chor ba /
NK113(e)002:198: chos thun ring drag pa sogs kyis sems skyo sun gyi dbang du song ba rnams spang ngo //
NK113(e)002:204: don go log tu 'dzin pa rnams spang ngo //
NK113(e)002:205: gnyis pa blang bya'i kun spyod la 'du shes bzhi brten pa /
NK113(e)002:206: pha rol tu phyin pa drug dang ldan pa /
NK113(e)002:208: dang po 'du shes bzhi brten pa na /
NK113(e)002:210: rigs kyi bu khyod kyis bdag nyid la nad pa'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK113(e)002:211: chos la sman gyi 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK113(e)002:212: nan tan nyams su len pa la nad nye bar 'tsho ba'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK113(e)002:213: dge ba'i bshes gnyen la sman pa mkhas pa'i 'du shes bskyed par bya'o //
NK113(e)002:215: pha rol tu phyin pa drug ni /
NK113(e)002:216: chos spyod thams cad kyi man ngag mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyud las /
NK113(e)002:217: me tog stan sogs rab 'bul zhing //
NK113(e)002:218: sa phyogs spyod lam sdom pa dang //
NK113(e)002:219: srog chags kun la 'tshe mi byed //
NK113(e)002:220: bla ma la ni gsol ba 'debs //
NK113(e)002:221: ma yengs bla ma'i gdams ngag nyan //
NK113(e)002:222: dogs sel phyir na skyon tshig 'dri //
NK113(e)002:223: sgrol ma yan lag drug dang ldan //
NK113(e)002:225: spyod lam gzhan bstan pa ni /
NK113(e)002:226: ma dad pa la chos mi bshad //
NK113(e)002:227: mi na bzhin du mgo dkris dang //
NK113(e)002:228: gdugs dang 'khar ba mtshon thogs dang //
NK113(e)002:229: mgo bo g.yogs pa dag la min //
NK113(e)002:231: gsum pa dpon slob de gnyis kyis 'chad nyan ji ltar bgyi ba'i tshul la /
NK113(e)002:232: chings chen po lnga'am gsum gyis bcings nas 'chad de /
NK113(e)002:233: dang po chings chen po lnga ni /
NK113(e)002:235: mdo don smra bar 'dod rnams la /
NK113(e)002:236: man ngag cung zhig sbyin par bya //
NK113(e)002:237: de la man ngag 'di yin te //
NK113(e)002:238: dgongs pa bsdus pa'i don bcas dang //
NK113(e)002:239: tshig don bcas dang mtshams sbyor bcas //
NK113(e)002:240: brgal lan bcas te bsnyad par bya //
NK113(e)002:243: dkyus kyis gcod pa stag mo'i mchongs stabs lta bu /
NK113(e)002:244: tshig gi 'bru non pa rus sbal gyi nur 'gros lta bu /
NK113(e)002:245: skabs kyi don bsdu ba seng ge'i 'gying lta bu'o //
NK113(e)002:246: gnyis pa bshad bya dngos bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK113(e)002:247: thog mar dge ba klad kyi don //
NK113(e)002:248: bar du dge ba gzhung gi don //
NK113(e)002:249: tha mar dge ba mjug gi don no //
NK113(e)002:250: dang po thog mar dge ba klad kyi don la gsum ste /
NK113(e)002:254: dang po mtshan don chings chen po lnga'i sgo nas 'chad pa la /
NK113(e)002:255: dang po dgos pa'i don ni /
NK113(e)002:256: dbang po rab rnams mtshan don shes pas gzhung don yongs rdzogs gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK113(e)002:257: 'bring rnams theg pa che chung gang gi phyogs su gtogs shes pa dang /
NK113(e)002:258: tha mas kyang ming don gyi 'brel ba shes nas
NK113(e)002:259: glegs bam 'tshol sla ba sogs kyi dgos pa yod
NK113(e)002:261: ming du gdags par ma mdzad na //
NK113(e)002:263: de bas mgon po thabs mkhas pas //
NK113(e)002:264: chos rnams ming du gdags par mdzad //
NK113(e)002:266: gnyis pa mtshams sbyor gyi don ni /
NK113(e)002:267: spyir chos gang dang gang 'chad kyang thob mar klad don nas 'chad dgos la /
NK113(e)002:268: de yang dang por mtshan smos pa 'byung ba yin la /
NK113(e)002:269: mtshan de yang chos la yid ches skye /
NK113(e)002:271: rgyud la byin rlabs 'jug pa ste /
NK113(e)002:272: dgos pa gsum dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK113(e)002:273: dang po mtshan rgya skad ltar smos pa ni /
NK113(e)002:275: gu na ko sha rat+na pra mo da brish+ti n+aa ma /
NK113(e)002:278: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba /
NK113(e)002:280: gu na zhes pa yon tan /
NK113(e)002:284: pra mo da brish+ti dga' ba'i char /
NK113(e)002:286: gsum pa tshig gi don ni /
NK113(e)002:287: skyes bu gsum gyi lam gyi rim pa thams cad
NK113(e)002:288: ma nor par nyams su blangs pa'i lam dang 'bras
NK113(e)002:289: bu'i yon tan thams cad ni yon tan /
NK113(e)002:290: de nyams su blangs pa las don gnyis kyi 'dod pa thams cad 'byung bas na rin po che /
NK113(e)002:291: de lta bu'i brjod bya phun sum tshogs pa'i tshig dang don gyi mdzod yin pas na mdzoda /
NK113(e)002:292: rang rgyud la legs byas dge ba'i lo tog bskyed
NK113(e)002:293: par 'dod pa'i skal ba bzang po'i gang zag thams
NK113(e)002:294: cad dga' bar byed pa'i char pa lta bu yin
NK113(e)002:296: zhes bya ba ni ming sgrog pa'o //
NK113(e)002:297: bzhi pa bsdus don gyi dbang du byas na /
NK113(e)002:298: yon tan rin po che'i mdzod ces bya ba ste /
NK113(e)002:299: lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan thams cad gang las 'byung ba'i mdzod lta bur gyur pa'o //
NK113(e)002:300: lnga pa brgal lan gyi don ni /
NK113(e)002:301: de la kha cig na re /
NK113(e)002:302: dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba mi 'thad de /
NK113(e)002:303: char yin dga' bar byed pa yin pas ma khyab ste /
NK113(e)002:305: klu dang yi dwags sogs la bye tshan gyi char sogs 'bebs pa'i phyir zer na /
NK113(e)002:306: 'dir dpe las mtshan du gsol ba'i dbang du byas
NK113(e)002:307: te gang dag dga' ba bskyed pa'i mtho ris lha
NK113(e)002:308: dang mi'i yul gyi char pa dag dper byed kyi
NK113(e)002:309: / ngan song gi char pa dper byed pa ma
NK113(e)002:310: yin pas rtsod pa de la snying po med do
NK113(e)002:311: / // gnyis pa mchod par brjod pa la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:312: mtshan smos pa'i sgo nas bsdus te mchod par brjod pa dang /
NK113(e)002:313: yon tan dran pa'i sgo nas rgyas par mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK113(e)002:317: 'byung ba dkon phyir dri med phyir //
NK113(e)002:318: mthu ldan phyir dang 'jig rten gyi //
NK113(e)002:319: rgyan gyur phyir dang mchog nyid phyir //
NK113(e)002:320: 'gyur ba med phyir dkon mchog nyid //
NK113(e)002:322: 'jig rten du sangs rgyas byon pa dang /
NK113(e)002:324: de nyams su len pa'i dge 'dun rnams ni 'jig
NK113(e)002:325: rten na u dum w+aa ra'i me tog dang nor
NK113(e)002:326: bu rin po che ltar 'byung ba dkon pa dang
NK113(e)002:327: / mi mthun nyes tshogs kyi dri ma med pa dang /
NK113(e)002:328: sgrib gnyis dang bdud bzhi sogs bcom pa'i mthu dang ldan pa dang /
NK113(e)002:329: gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi phun sum tshogs pa
NK113(e)002:330: thams cad bskyed pa'i rgyu yin pas 'jig rten gyi
NK113(e)002:332: 'gro ba lha dang bcas pa'i mgon du bzhugs shing
NK113(e)002:333: srid zhi'i khams na 'gran zla dang bral bas na
NK113(e)002:334: mchog nyid dang / gnas skabs kun tu yon tan
NK113(e)002:335: gyi rang bzhin nyams pa med cing thugs rje rgyun
NK113(e)002:336: chad med pas na 'gyur ba med pa ste dkona
NK113(e)002:337: mchog nyid dang / mchoga ces bya'o // gsum la zhes pa ni /
NK113(e)002:338: sangs rgyas dang chos dang dge 'dun te /
NK113(e)002:339: dang po sangs rgyas la ngo bo /
NK113(e)002:343: dang po spangs rtogs kyi yon tan thams cad mthar phyin pa sangs rgyas kyi ngo bo /
NK113(e)002:345: ma rig pa'i gnyis 'thug po lta bu sangs shing
NK113(e)002:346: shes bya'i chos la blo gros kyi pad+mo rnam par
NK113(e)002:347: rgyas pas na sangs rgyas zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:352: bud+d+ha khong du chud pa la'o zhes pas shes bya
NK113(e)002:353: thams cad mkhyen cing khong du chud pas na sangs
NK113(e)002:354: rgyas so // gnyis pa chos la'ang snga ma ltar bzhi las /
NK113(e)002:355: nyon shes kyi sgrib pa gang rung spang ba'am spong
NK113(e)002:356: byed kyi thabs su gyur pa chos kyi ngo bo
NK113(e)002:358: nad la smad gtong ba ltar rang rgyud kyi nyon mongs pa 'chos pas na chos so //
NK113(e)002:359: dbye na lung dang rtogs pa'i chos sam /
NK113(e)002:360: 'gog lam gyi bden pa gnyis so //
NK113(e)002:362: d+har+m+aa zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na 'dzin pa ste
NK113(e)002:363: 'khor ba dang ngan song gi lam du mi gtong
NK113(e)002:364: zhing / yang dag pa'i lam du 'dzin pas na chos so //
NK113(e)002:365: gsum pa dge 'dun la'ang bzhi ste /
NK113(e)002:366: rig grol gyi yon tan gnyis dang ldan pa dge 'dun gyi ngo bo /
NK113(e)002:368: yang dag pa dge ba'i lam dang rang rgyud mi phyed par 'dus pas na dge 'dun no //
NK113(e)002:369: dbye na theg dman nyan rang gi dge 'dun dang /
NK113(e)002:370: theg chen byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun no //
NK113(e)002:372: sad+ga zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na 'dus pa ste /
NK113(e)002:373: 'gro ba lha dang bcas pas lam las mi phyed pas na dge 'dun no //
NK113(e)002:374: phyag 'tshal lo zhes pa lta ba mjal ba /
NK113(e)002:376: mos gus kyi phyag ste blo mchog rnams kyis ni
NK113(e)002:377: rnam pa gsum ka tshang ba'i sgo nas phyag mdzad
NK113(e)002:378: pa'o // gnyis pa yon tan dran pa'i sgo nas rgyas par mchod par brjod pa ni /
NK113(e)002:379: rat+na zhes pa'i sgra las drangs na rin chen te 'jig rten na 'byung bar dkon pa dang /
NK113(e)002:380: mchog tu gyur pa la sogs pa'i chos mtshungs drug
NK113(e)002:381: gi sgo nas bzhag pa'i dkon mchog rnam pa gsum
NK113(e)002:382: ni bsod nams kyi sa bon bskyed pa'i zhi /
NK113(e)002:383: 'gro ba thams cad la mnyes gshin pa'i skyabs kha na ma tho ba med par bzhugs pa /
NK113(e)002:385: 'phags pa'i bden pa bzhi la gnas pa /
NK113(e)002:387: mu stegs can dang bdud sdig can gyi rgol ba ngan pas gsung dang /
NK113(e)002:393: stobs dang mi 'jigs pa la sogs pa mtha' dag
NK113(e)002:394: gi 'byung gnas yin pa'i gragsa pasa 'jig rten sum
NK113(e)002:395: po thams cad khyab pa la /
NK113(e)002:396: de'i rang bzhin brda sprod pa 'i phyir ston pa'i
NK113(e)002:397: sku gzugs dang tshigs su bcad pa ras la bkod
NK113(e)002:398: pa'i spring yiga gi rnam pa bskur ba mthong ba
NK113(e)002:399: tsam gyis kyang bu mo mu tig 'khri shing bsam
NK113(e)002:400: gtan dgongs pa gcig pa lta bu'i raba tu dga'
NK113(e)002:401: ba nyams su myongs shing dad de de'i don la
NK113(e)002:402: bsam par byas nasa thar lam la bar du gcod
NK113(e)002:403: pa'i mthong spang sgro btags kyi rtog pa bdud kyi
NK113(e)002:404: bu mo'i bslu byed kyi bzhin ras kun+da'i tshal mthong
NK113(e)002:405: lam ye shes kyi nyi mas skal ba ngan par
NK113(e)002:406: byas te drungs nas 'byin pa'i tshul gyis spangs nas
NK113(e)002:407: nyon mongs dang rtog pa lhan skyes sgom spang gi
NK113(e)002:408: cha rnams spong bar bgyid pa la mngon par phyogsa
NK113(e)002:409: pa ni sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje'i mthu las byung
NK113(e)002:410: ba de'i phyir / dkon mchog gsum gyi rgyu 'bras
NK113(e)002:411: mtha' dag dang 'brel ba'i chos kyi gtam yang dag
NK113(e)002:412: pa ni 'gro ba mtha' dag gis mnyan par 'os
NK113(e)002:413: shing srid pa'i rang bzhin nyon mongs pa dang rnam
NK113(e)002:414: par rtog pa'i gnyen por che bas na de skad
NK113(e)002:415: ces gzugs can gyi rgyan du bkod do //
NK113(e)002:418: bstan bcos byed pos ston pa la //
NK113(e)002:419: mchod par brjod pa 'bras med min //
NK113(e)002:420: ston pa dang ni bstan bcos la //
NK113(e)002:421: dad 'dun bskyed par byed phyir ro //
NK113(e)002:423: de dag gi tshul sngon byung gi gtam ni /
NK113(e)002:425: nor chen zhes bya'i tshong pa ni //
NK113(e)002:426: b+aa ra n+aa s+air sngon byung gyur //
NK113(e)002:427: de yi khyim thab bsod nams can //
NK113(e)002:428: rin chen ldan zhes bya bar gyur //
NK113(e)002:429: bdag po lnga pa nyid gyur tshe //
NK113(e)002:430: bu med de yis mchod rten rtser //
NK113(e)002:431: do shal chen po gus ldan pas //
NK113(e)002:432: mchod pa byas nas phul bar gyur //
NK113(e)002:433: bsod nams rnam smin das de nyid //
NK113(e)002:434: sing ga la yi bdag po yi //
NK113(e)002:435: bu mo mu tig 'khri shing gyur //
NK113(e)002:436: de nyid skye ba gzhan la ni //
NK113(e)002:437: phyug pas rgyags shing rmongs gyur nas //
NK113(e)002:438: mchod pa smod cing sgrin gyur pa //
NK113(e)002:439: de yis yun ring 'bangs mor gyur //
NK113(e)002:440: dge dag mi dge'i las gang gang //
NK113(e)002:441: skye ba'i zhing la skye bos btab //
NK113(e)002:442: ces pa ltar nor chen gyi chung ma de sh+aakya'i
NK113(e)002:443: khyim du 'bangs mo ro hi ta'am skyed ma zhes
NK113(e)002:445: bcom ldan 'das kyis nya gro d+ha'i kun dga' ra
NK113(e)002:446: bar chos bstan pa na sh+aakya ming chen gyi chung
NK113(e)002:447: ma rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan te song nas chos
NK113(e)002:448: mnyan pa'i phyir bsdad pa dang 'dod chags dang ma
NK113(e)002:449: bral ba rnams chags pa skyes so //
NK113(e)002:450: tshul de kun dga' bos ming chen gyi chung ma
NK113(e)002:451: la smras pas chung mas rgyan rnams bkrol te bran
NK113(e)002:452: mo skyed ma la khyim du skyel du bcug go
NK113(e)002:453: // ji tsam na sh+aakya'i bu mo zhig rang gi
NK113(e)002:454: mgul pa na mu tig gi do shal zhig yod
NK113(e)002:455: pa la rtog cing lag nom byed pa las chos
NK113(e)002:456: la sems mi gtad pa mthong nas de'i nga rgyal
NK113(e)002:457: bcag pa'i phyir bran mo skyes ma la yang kho
NK113(e)002:458: mo'i mu tig gi do shal de slar khyer te
NK113(e)002:459: shog smras pas de'i kyi hud bran mo'i rigs 'di
NK113(e)002:460: // re sdug / sangs rgyas kyi zhal blta ba dang /
NK113(e)002:461: chos mnyam pa 'di tsam yang mi khom mo snyam mo //
NK113(e)002:462: bcom ldan 'das kyis de la dgongs nas rdzu 'phrul gyis gro ga la /
NK113(e)002:463: dge ma skye ba 'byung ba ni //
NK113(e)002:464: 'jig pa yin par bsam nas su //
NK113(e)002:465: ngas gsungs pa yi dge ba la //
NK113(e)002:466: brtson 'grus bskyes nas mnyam par bya //
NK113(e)002:468: de nas de dga' zhing mgu nas tshigs su bcad
NK113(e)002:469: pa smra bzhin sangs rgyas la dmigs pa kho nas
NK113(e)002:470: song ba na ba drus ma zhig gis bsad do
NK113(e)002:471: // de sangs rgyas la dad bzhin shi bas sing
NK113(e)002:472: ga la'i rgyal po'i btsun mo'i mngal du zhugs so
NK113(e)002:473: // // gang gi tshe nying mtshams sbyar ba de'i tshe der mu tig gi char babs so //
NK113(e)002:474: zla ba tshang nas btsas pa'i tshe yang mu tig
NK113(e)002:475: gi char babs pas de'i ming la mu tig can
NK113(e)002:476: nam mu tig 'khri shing zhes btags so //
NK113(e)002:478: mnyan yod kyi tshong pa rnams kyis gru bo che
NK113(e)002:479: bsgrubs nas rgya mtshor zhugs te der phyin cing bsdad
NK113(e)002:480: nas mdo sde'i tshigs su bcad pa bton pa bu
NK113(e)002:481: mo'i thos so // de nas de dag pho brang
NK113(e)002:482: du bkug ste yul dbus kyi glu de longs shig
NK113(e)002:483: mo'i thos so // ces smras / de dag gis smras pa /
NK113(e)002:484: glu ma yin sangs rgyas kyi gsung yin no zhes byas /
NK113(e)002:485: sangs rgyas zhes bya ba'i mtshan de thos nas snying
NK113(e)002:486: dga' bas ba spu thams cad zing zhes byed de
NK113(e)002:487: ngo mtshar skyes nas sangs rgyas zhes bya ba'i rgyu
NK113(e)002:489: de dag gis kyang ji lta ba bzhin bshad do //
NK113(e)002:490: de de'i rkyen gyis sngon pas dga' ba rgya chen
NK113(e)002:491: po thob nas bcom ldan 'das la gsol ba'i spring
NK113(e)002:492: yig phul lo // thams cad mkhyen pa bcom ldan
NK113(e)002:493: 'das kyis mkhyen bzhin du spring yig bklags pa'i don
NK113(e)002:494: yig phul lo // / kye ma bsod nams tshong
NK113(e)002:495: zong dag gis rnyed par gyur pa khyod ni dran
NK113(e)002:496: yig phul lo // / pa nyid // rgud dang
NK113(e)002:497: gdung ba dang ni sred pa 'joms pa'i srid pa'i
NK113(e)002:499: bcom ldan las byung gtam gyis nyer bskrun yang dag rig pa myong ba'i sa //
NK113(e)002:500: bcom ldan 'di de bdag gi bdud rtsi yang dag bgo skal chen por gyur ba yin //
NK113(e)002:501: zhes pa nyid du gzigs nas ri mo mkhan rnams
NK113(e)002:502: la sku'i gzugs brnyan brir bcug pa na bri ma
NK113(e)002:503: nus nas 'od btang ste tshon rtsi sna tshogs kyis
NK113(e)002:505: de'i 'og tu gsum la skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK113(e)002:507: rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i yan lag bcu gnyis po lugs dang mthun pa dang /
NK113(e)002:508: lugs dang mi mthun pa dang 'phags pa'i lam yan lag brgyad pa bris so //
NK113(e)002:510: tshigs su bcad pa gnyis po /
NK113(e)002:511: brtsam par bya zhing dbyung bar bya //
NK113(e)002:512: sangs rgyas bstan la 'jug par bya //
NK113(e)002:513: 'dam bu'i khyim na glang chen bzhin //
NK113(e)002:514: 'chi bdag sde ni gzhom par bya //
NK113(e)002:515: gang zhig rab tu bag yod pas //
NK113(e)002:517: skye ba'i 'khor ba rab spangs nas //
NK113(e)002:518: sdug bsngal tha mar byed par 'gyur //
NK113(e)002:520: sing ga la'i rgyal po la bka' yig springs pa /
NK113(e)002:521: der gnas kyi skye bo thams cad bsdus la bkur sti chen pos thang sku shoms shig /
NK113(e)002:522: tshong ba rnams la bka' stsal pa /
NK113(e)002:523: mu tig can sangs rgyas kyi sku dang /
NK113(e)002:524: 'og tu skyabs su 'gro ba sogs nas /
NK113(e)002:525: bdud rtsi rtogs pa'i lam dang /
NK113(e)002:526: gong gi tshigs bcad gnyis po lam la brtson pas
NK113(e)002:527: sdug bsngal las grol ba'i don rnams brjod cig gsungs
NK113(e)002:528: nas bskur ro // tshong pa rnams kyis bka' bzhin
NK113(e)002:529: 'tshal zhes song nas rgyal po la yi ge byin
NK113(e)002:530: nas bskur ro // no // rgyal pos kyang bka' yig gi nang bzhin thar sku bshams pas /
NK113(e)002:531: skye bo'i tshogs thams cad kyis sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal lo zhes gsangs bstod de brjod do //
NK113(e)002:532: mu tig can dad pa dran pos ba spu zing
NK113(e)002:533: zhes byed cing mig mchi mas gang bzhin tshong pa
NK113(e)002:534: rnams la ris su bris pa de'i don dris pa
NK113(e)002:535: na de dag gis kyang ji lta ba bzhin du
NK113(e)002:536: brjod do // de nas bu mos rten cing 'brel bar 'byung ba'i don la bsam par brtsam pas /
NK113(e)002:537: khrag dang mchi ma'i rgya mtsho chen po ni bskams /
NK113(e)002:538: rus pa'i ri bo chen po ni bcom /
NK113(e)002:539: 'jig tshogs la lta ba'i ri'i rtse mo nyi shu
NK113(e)002:540: mtho ba ye shes kyi rdo rjes bcom nas chos
NK113(e)002:541: rnams la chos kyi mig rdul med cing dri ma
NK113(e)002:542: dang bral ba rnam par dag pa thob ste rgyun
NK113(e)002:543: du zhugs pa'i 'bras bu mngon sum du byas te
NK113(e)002:544: / des bden pa mthong nas tshigs su bcad pas smras pa /
NK113(e)002:545: ring na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK113(e)002:546: shes rab mig ni rnam sbyangs pas //
NK113(e)002:548: sman mkhas de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK113(e)002:549: ring na bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyis //
NK113(e)002:550: lta ba'i ri bo drungs phyung ste //
NK113(e)002:551: lta ba'i zug rngu sel mdzad pa //
NK113(e)002:552: sman mkhas de la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK113(e)002:554: mchog gsum la mu tig bre gsum bskur nas skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK113(e)002:555: bslab pa'i gzhi lnga la gnas par gsol zhes kyang byas so //
NK113(e)002:556: sku gzugs de la thang sku 'od zer ma zhes bris sku thams cad kyi thog mar grags so //
NK113(e)002:557: gsum pa rtsom par dam bca' ba la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:558: dam pa'i chos 'dzin pa'i phan yon la bsam ste rtsom par dam bca' ba dang /
NK113(e)002:559: dam pa chos mi 'dzin pa'i nyes dmigs la bsam ste rtsam par dam bca' ba'o //
NK113(e)002:561: 'di ltar shes bya thams cad mkhyen pa'i blo gros
NK113(e)002:562: mchog mnga' ba thub pa chen pos phun sum tshogs
NK113(e)002:563: pa lngas bstan pa'i mdo sngags kyi sde snod dpag
NK113(e)002:565: thub pa'i rjes 'jug 'phags pa'i gang zag rnams kyis chings chen po lngas 'brel dgod /
NK113(e)002:566: dgos 'brel yan lag bzhis gtan la phab pa'i bstan
NK113(e)002:567: bcos tshig don gyi yon tan du mas brgyan pa
NK113(e)002:568: dag byed chu'i gter rgya mtsho chen po lta bu
NK113(e)002:569: gcig tu barlinga zhing zab la gting dpag dka' ba
NK113(e)002:570: rnams la brten nas rgyal ba'i bstan pa yun ring
NK113(e)002:573: chos rnams thams cad bka' dang bstan bcos gnyis //
NK113(e)002:574: legs par gsungs dang de yi dgongs 'grel pa //
NK113(e)002:575: de yi dbang gis sh+aakya'i bstan pa 'di //
NK113(e)002:576: 'jig rten khams 'dir yun ring gnas par 'gyur //
NK113(e)002:578: de lta bu'i bka' dang dgongs 'grel gnyis po ma nyams par mchis bzhin pa yin na /
NK113(e)002:579: rgyu gsum ma tshang ba'i gyi nar smra ba dag
NK113(e)002:580: gi spyi brtol gyis byas pa'i bstan bcos la 'chos
NK113(e)002:581: skyob kyi yon tan gnyis dang nang pa'i tshul gsum
NK113(e)002:582: nyung zhing phyi rol pa'i ngan pa drug gis lhad
NK113(e)002:583: kyang srid pa'i nags stug po'i gcong rong gi 'bab
NK113(e)002:584: chu rlabs phreng gi 'ur sgras gnod pa can bzhin
NK113(e)002:585: du bstan bcos rtsom pa'i ca co sgrogas pa 'di
NK113(e)002:586: mdzes pa mi ngo ma pa'i gnas su mthong ba
NK113(e)002:587: yanga chos tshul rgya mtsho mang du thos pa'i yon
NK113(e)002:590: sngon chad ma byung ba yang 'dir brjod med //
NK113(e)002:591: sdeb sbyor mkhas pa'ang bdag la yod min te //
NK113(e)002:592: de phyir gzhan don bsam pa'ang bdag la med //
NK113(e)002:593: rang gi yid la goms phyir ngas 'di brtsams //
NK113(e)002:595: de la 'chos skyob kyi yon tan gnyis ni /
NK113(e)002:597: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang /
NK113(e)002:598: ngan 'gro'i srid las skyob byed gang yin pa //
NK113(e)002:599: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK113(e)002:600: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK113(e)002:602: yon tan dang ldan pa'i bstan bcos de'i rang bzhin ni /
NK113(e)002:607: bstan bcos drug bral gsum dang ldan //
NK113(e)002:609: rnam par grol ba'i don med pa la sogs pa'i phyi rol pa'i ngan pa drug dang bral zhing /
NK113(e)002:612: sdug bsngal spong ba ste nang pa'i tshul gsum dang ldan pa'o //
NK113(e)002:613: gong du bshad pa de lta na yang dam pa'i
NK113(e)002:614: chos kyi brjod bya yang dag pa la brten pa'i
NK113(e)002:615: slad kyis manyana par 'osa pa'i tshul /
NK113(e)002:617: ji ltar bde gshegs sku gzugs shing las kyang //
NK113(e)002:618: bgyis pa ci 'dra'ang rung ste mkhas pas mchod //
NK113(e)002:619: de bzhin bdag gi snyan dngags 'di ngan yang //
NK113(e)002:620: dam chos brjod la bsten slad smad ma bgyi //
NK113(e)002:622: de ltar bshad cing nyan pa'i dgos pa yang //
NK113(e)002:624: thos pas chos rnams shes par byed //
NK113(e)002:625: thos pas sdig las ldog par byed //
NK113(e)002:626: thos pas don ma yin pa spong //
NK113(e)002:627: thos pas mya ngan 'das pa thob //
NK113(e)002:629: dge slong dag gang zag gnyis po 'dis bsod nams
NK113(e)002:630: mang po bskyed de sdig pa'i rtsa ba 'byin cing
NK113(e)002:632: bdud kyi rgyal mtshan snyol bar byed /
NK113(e)002:633: chos kyi rgyal mtshan bsgreng bar byed /
NK113(e)002:634: de bzhin gshegs pa'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar byed do //
NK113(e)002:636: gang gus par byas te chos 'chad pa dang /
NK113(e)002:637: gang 'di na gus par byas te chos nyan pa'o //
NK113(e)002:639: de'i phyir bdag cag gi ston pas sngon slob pa
NK113(e)002:640: lam gyi dus su lus la lcags gzer stong btab
NK113(e)002:641: pa dang / sha la kong bu stong brus nas
NK113(e)002:642: me spar ba la sogs pa'i dka' ba chen po'i
NK113(e)002:643: sgo nas chos tshigs su bcad pa re re tsam
NK113(e)002:644: mnyan pa la sogs pa lta bu'i tshul la bsam
NK113(e)002:645: ste bung bas me tog gi bcud la myang ba
NK113(e)002:646: bzhin 'og nas 'byung tshul mnyan pa la spro bar
NK113(e)002:647: pa dang / bya'o // gnyis pa dam pa'i chos
NK113(e)002:648: mi 'dzin pa'i nyes dmigs la bsam nas rtsom par
NK113(e)002:649: pa dang / bya'o // dam bca' ni / dus
NK113(e)002:650: thog ma med pa nas bdag tu 'dzin pa dang
NK113(e)002:651: nyon mongs pas bskyed pa'i mngal la sogs pa bzhi
NK113(e)002:653: na tshod 'gyur ba'i rga ba dang /
NK113(e)002:654: 'du ba bslad pa'i na ba dang /
NK113(e)002:655: srog btang ba'i 'chi ba la sogs pa yi rimsa
NK113(e)002:656: nad kyisa da lta'i bar du bataba par gyur nas
NK113(e)002:657: 'jig rten ma rungs par byas kyang de'i gnyen por
NK113(e)002:658: gyur pa'i rnam grol gyi lam dang ma 'phrad la
NK113(e)002:659: / da lta chos dar ba'i yul du skyes shing
NK113(e)002:660: dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang 'phrad nas sman chen po
NK113(e)002:662: dang po thos pa'i dus su mi dad pa dad par byed pa rna ba'i bdud rtsi /
NK113(e)002:663: bar du bsam pa'i dus su mi dga' ba dga'
NK113(e)002:664: bar byed cing rnam g.yeng gi gnyen por 'gyur pa
NK113(e)002:665: / tha ma bsgom pa'i dus su ma grol ba
NK113(e)002:666: grol bar byed cing blo rnam par grol ba'i shes
NK113(e)002:667: rab skyed par byed pa'i dam pa'i chos lag tu
NK113(e)002:668: mchis shing nyams su len pa'i skal ba dang ldan
NK113(e)002:670: thos pas thob par mi byed /
NK113(e)002:671: bsam pas mngon du mi spyod /
NK113(e)002:672: sgom pas 'dzin par mi byed cing khyi'i mdun du
NK113(e)002:673: r+ts+wa bzhag pa ltar spong bar byed pa'i nyes pa
NK113(e)002:674: ni nad kyis tshabs cher btab pa'i skyes bu sman
NK113(e)002:675: pa las byol nas mya ngam gyi thang du 'bad
NK113(e)002:676: pas 'khyams pa lta bu yin te /
NK113(e)002:678: dam chos thang ma bzhin du brdal ba la //
NK113(e)002:679: sdig pa bab col du byed pa shin tu blun //
NK113(e)002:682: gang zhig skye nad rga shi sel ba'i bdud rtsi de //
NK113(e)002:683: thob par mi byed mi spyod 'dzin par mi byed pa //
NK113(e)002:684: de dag nyes mang gti mug 'thibs pos bslad pa ste /
NK113(e)002:685: yun ring nad kyis thebs pa sman chen mi bsten bzhin //
NK113(e)002:687: 'gro ba kun gyi mig gcig dri ma med pa gang //
NK113(e)002:688: de ni sa rnam gsum po'i spyi mthun sgron ma ste //
NK113(e)002:689: bstan pa bde legs rnyed nas gang zhig 'dor ba de //
NK113(e)002:690: gti mug shin tu rmad byung dag gis gtses par zad //
NK113(e)002:692: des na de 'dra ba'i skye bo rnamas la bdag
NK113(e)002:693: gisa rim dgu'i theg pa'i don thams cad bstan bcos
NK113(e)002:694: kyi gzhung gcig tu bsdus pa'i gdams ngag 'di ji
NK113(e)002:695: ltar 'domsa te don du 'gyur dka' bas so //
NK113(e)002:696: 'on kyang brtse bas gdul bya rjes su mi 'dor
NK113(e)002:697: bar brtsam par dam bca' ba'i skabs dbye bar mdzad
NK113(e)002:699: ngas ni khyod la thar pa'i thabs bstan gyi //
NK113(e)002:700: thar pa rang la rag las brtson par gyis //
NK113(e)002:702: skabs 'dir dgos 'brel yan lag bzhi 'chad pa'i srol ltar na /
NK113(e)002:703: spyir ngag tsam la yod pa'i dgos 'brel dang /
NK113(e)002:704: dgos 'brel ngag la yod pa'i dgos 'brel dang /
NK113(e)002:705: bstan bcos lus la yod pa'i dgos 'brel rnams yod kyang /
NK113(e)002:706: don bstan bcos lus la yod pa'i dgos 'brel yin pas /
NK113(e)002:707: skyes bu gsum gyi lam rim gyi nyams len rnams ni brjod bya /
NK113(e)002:708: de lta bu'i brjod bya dang ldan pa'i bstan bcos
NK113(e)002:709: 'di thos bsam gyis gtan la phab nas thar par
NK113(e)002:710: 'gro ba'i lam ma nor bar shes pa ni dgos
NK113(e)002:711: pa / de ltar shes nas nyams su blangs pas mthar thug gi 'bras bu 'grub pa nying dgos /
NK113(e)002:712: de gsum gcig la gcig brten gyis 'brel ba grub pa ni 'brel pa'o //
NK113(e)002:713: gnyis pa bar du dge ba gzhung gi don la bsdus don gsungs tshul rnam pa gsum ste /
NK113(e)002:716: las rgyu 'bras bsam pa'i le'u gsum blo chos su 'gro bar byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK113(e)002:717: le'u bzhi pa nas dgu pa'i bar gyis chos de yang thar pa tsam gyi lam dang /
NK113(e)002:718: de thabs shes kyis zin pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i lam du 'gro bar byed pa'i thabs dang /
NK113(e)002:719: bcu pas lam de yang blang dor gyi mtshan mar
NK113(e)002:720: lta ba'i 'khrul pa zad par byed pa'i thabs dang
NK113(e)002:721: / le'u phyi ma gsum gyis 'khrul snang thams cad
NK113(e)002:722: dag pa rab 'byams su blta ba'ang gnyis su med
NK113(e)002:723: pa'i ye shes su 'char bar byed pa'i thabs su
NK113(e)002:724: / bshad pa dang / yang le'u dang po gnyis kyis 'khor bar zhen log gi nges 'byung /
NK113(e)002:725: gsum pa dang bzhi pas las 'bras yid ches kyi dad pa /
NK113(e)002:726: lnga pa nas dgu pa'i bar gyis gzhan phan don gnyer gyi byang sems /
NK113(e)002:727: bcu pas snang srid rnam dag gi dag snang /
NK113(e)002:728: phyi ma gsum gyis rtsol med rang bzhag gi dran
NK113(e)002:729: pa skyong ba'i thabs rnams bstan pa yin zhes gsungs
NK113(e)002:730: te don la de gnyis gang zag gcig 'tshang rgya
NK113(e)002:731: ba'i lam du 'chad pa la mtshungs so //
NK113(e)002:732: skabs 'dir bsdus don gsungs tshul gang gi rjes su 'brang ba la gsum ste /
NK113(e)002:733: chos la blo 'jug pa'i rgyu dal 'byor rnyed dka' ba bshad pa dang /
NK113(e)002:734: brtson 'grus kyi lcag 'debs pa'i don du tshe mi rtag pa bsgom pa bshad pa dang /
NK113(e)002:735: nyams su blang bya skyes bu gsum gyi lam rim rgya cher bshad pa'o //
NK113(e)002:736: dang po blo chos la 'jug pa'i rgyu dal 'byor rnyed dka' bsgom pa'i le'u la lnga ste /
NK113(e)002:737: mi lus rnam par dbye ba /
NK113(e)002:738: 'gal zla mi khom pa brgyad bshad pa /
NK113(e)002:739: dal 'byor gyi rang bzhin ngos gzung ba /
NK113(e)002:740: rnyed dka' ba'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa /
NK113(e)002:741: gdams ngag brjod pas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK113(e)002:743: dus ring po nasa 'grogs shing nyes dmigs mi shes
NK113(e)002:744: par phan pa'i gnas su btas nas bshes par gyur
NK113(e)002:745: pa 'khor ba'i gnas bsdi pa tsam nas sdug bsngal
NK113(e)002:748: legs par spyad kyang sdig dang 'dres pa /
NK113(e)002:749: byed pa mang zhing 'bras bu nyung ba /
NK113(e)002:750: so ma btang ba'i chu snod ltar 'jig sla bas yon tan gyi phyogs mi 'dzin pa /
NK113(e)002:751: lus srog la nye zhe shin tu yod pa 'broga
NK113(e)002:752: dgona pa lta bu gang du sngar yang lan grangsa
NK113(e)002:753: du mar mgo dang yan lag bcad pa la sogs
NK113(e)002:754: pa'i sdug bsngal gyi tshor ba drag pos gnod pas
NK113(e)002:755: lus sems gdung bar byas shing phyin chad kyang de
NK113(e)002:756: 'dra ba'i sdug bsngal gyis gdon mi za bar gdung
NK113(e)002:757: bar 'gyur ba'i las du ma lkoga tu gyur nas
NK113(e)002:758: yod pa mi shes pa rnams dam pa rnams kyis
NK113(e)002:759: basngagasa pa ma byas pa'i gnas der mi skyo bar
NK113(e)002:760: ma zad da dung yang 'gyur ba'i rang bzhin mtho
NK113(e)002:761: ris kyi bde ba snying po med cing nyes dmigs
NK113(e)002:762: dang ldan pa 'di la shin tu sred cing dge
NK113(e)002:763: sdig gi 'jug ldog gang yang mi shes par rmongsa
NK113(e)002:764: pa'i dbang gis sdig pa'i las thabs 'ba' zhig gis
NK113(e)002:765: tshe gang po 'da' bar byed pa rnams la ni
NK113(e)002:766: mi lus tsam po ba zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:767: yang rab tu byung ba'i rtags ma blangs pa'am /
NK113(e)002:768: blangs kyang rung ste res 'ga' ni chos la spyod
NK113(e)002:769: pa ltar snang yang rgyun chags pa ni khyim gyi
NK113(e)002:771: phyugs kyi 'tsho skyong sogs sdig pa'i bsam sbyor dang shin tu 'dres pa rnams ni /
NK113(e)002:772: slob dpon ma ti tsi tras /
NK113(e)002:773: dga' bar bgyid pa'i yul rnams dang //
NK113(e)002:774: rgyags par bgyid pa'i lang tsho dang //
NK113(e)002:775: bdag nyid rang dgar spyod pa de //
NK113(e)002:776: kun tu don med bgyid pa'i sgo //
NK113(e)002:777: zhes pa ltar ngan song du 'bab cing gzhol bar
NK113(e)002:778: 'gyur kyang ngan song gi 'gro ba phal pa dang
NK113(e)002:779: / mi lus tsam po ba las cung zad 'phags
NK113(e)002:780: te thar pa'i sa bon dang ldan pas mi lus
NK113(e)002:781: khyad par ba zhes bya ste /
NK113(e)002:782: nam mkha' rin po che'i mdo las /
NK113(e)002:783: sems can gyi khams na gang dag chos 'di pa dag tu ma zhugs pa'am /
NK113(e)002:784: zhugs kyang rung ste dge ba dang mi dge ba
NK113(e)002:785: 'dres mar spyod cing 'du 'dzi dang rnam par geyanga
NK113(e)002:786: ba lhur len pas lus dang ngag dang yid mi
NK113(e)002:787: bskrun zhing 'phyar ba ngan song gsum du 'bab cing
NK113(e)002:788: ngan 'gror gzhol ba'i las can de dag kyang /
NK113(e)002:789: sangs rgyas kyi thugs rje nyi ma'i 'od kyis gzigs
NK113(e)002:790: te yun ring mo zhig na thar pa'i sa bon
NK113(e)002:791: dang ldan pas / de'i phyir mi lus khyad par can zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:793: gnyis pa 'gal zla mi khom pa brgyad bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK113(e)002:798: de ltar bsam sbyor mi dge bas rgyud brlag cing
NK113(e)002:799: dal 'byor don med du byed pa de ni mtho
NK113(e)002:800: ba'i gnas 'di nas slar yang gnas ngan du ltung
NK113(e)002:801: bar 'gyur la / gang du zhe na /
NK113(e)002:805: dbang bo ma tshang ba dang /
NK113(e)002:806: lta ba phyin ci loga tu gyur pa dang /
NK113(e)002:807: sangsa rgyas 'byung ba med pa'i gnas dag tu 'khyamsa par 'gyur ro //
NK113(e)002:808: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:809: mi ma yin pa'i mi khom pa dang /
NK113(e)002:810: mir gyur pa'i mi khom pa bshad pa'o //
NK113(e)002:815: lha tshe ring po bshad pa'o //
NK113(e)002:817: 'di ltar thang cig tsam yang ngal bso ba'am bag
NK113(e)002:818: yangs pa'i skabsa batsala du yod pa ma yin par
NK113(e)002:819: lcagsa bsregas kyi sa gzhir ral gri dang tho ba
NK113(e)002:820: la sogs pa'i mtshon cha drag po thogs pa can
NK113(e)002:821: gyi gshin rje'i skyes bu shin tu sdang ba dang
NK113(e)002:822: ldan pa rnams dang me mtshon sogs kyi char pa
NK113(e)002:823: 'bab pa chada pa rtsub mos lan gcig ma yin
NK113(e)002:824: par yang dang yang du srog 'phroga pa tsam gyi
NK113(e)002:825: sdug bsngal drag po gtad kyang sngon las ngan pa'i
NK113(e)002:826: rnam par smin pa ma zad kyi bar du 'chi
NK113(e)002:827: bar mi nusa pa'i dmyala ba pa rnams da dung
NK113(e)002:828: yang byed pa rgyu mthun gyi 'bras bu khong khro'i
NK113(e)002:829: las ngan pa'i rnyi la 'thogas nas tshe'i tshad ni
NK113(e)002:831: des mtshon nas grang dmyal la sogs pa'i gnas su
NK113(e)002:832: skyes kyang chos kyi rten du khom pa'i gnas skabs
NK113(e)002:833: med pa'o // gnyis pa yi dwags ni /
NK113(e)002:834: spyi mthun gyi sgrib pa can tha na rnag khraga
NK113(e)002:835: dang phyi sa sogas mi gtsang ba ngan ngon tsam
NK113(e)002:836: dag kyang mi rnyed pa'i yi dwagsa rnams ni zas
NK113(e)002:837: skom gyis phongsa nas bkres shing skom pa'i sdug bsngal
NK113(e)002:838: gyis nyama thag pa smos ci dgosa /
NK113(e)002:839: phyi'i sgrib pa can ni chu klung dang shing ljon
NK113(e)002:840: pa lo tog dang ldan pa rnams la'ang bltas pa'i
NK113(e)002:841: moda tsam la skamsa pa dang /
NK113(e)002:842: bza' btung gi longs spyod mang po mthong nas drung
NK113(e)002:843: du bsnyegs pa na skyes bu go mtshon thogs pa
NK113(e)002:844: mang pos bsrung ste longs spyod du mi ster ba'o
NK113(e)002:845: // nang gi sgrib pa can ni kha khab mig
NK113(e)002:846: tsam la lto ba yul ljongs tsam pa sogs mgo
NK113(e)002:848: bza' btung cung zad khong du song bas nanga khrola 'tshiga pa'i sdug zad mi shes pa myong ba'o //
NK113(e)002:849: sgos khur gyi sgrib pa can ni /
NK113(e)002:850: gcig gi lus la mang pos tshang bcas pa dang /
NK113(e)002:851: mgrin par wa ba rdol ba dang /
NK113(e)002:852: phan tshun gdong du 'tshogs nas rma byung ba'i rnag khrag gis kha zas byed pa la sogs pa'o //
NK113(e)002:853: mkha' la rgyu ba ni btsan dang the'u rang la
NK113(e)002:854: sogs pa rtag tu 'jigs skrag gis gdung zhing sngar
NK113(e)002:855: gang gis shi ba'i sdug bsngal de zhag bdun bdun
NK113(e)002:857: gzhan la bsam sbyor ngan pa'i rgyus shi ma thag
NK113(e)002:858: dmyal bar ltung ba la sogs bas sdug bsngal lo
NK113(e)002:859: // spyir yi dwags kyi tshe tshad ni /
NK113(e)002:860: mi yi zla ba zhag cig tu brtsis pa'i rang lo lnga brgya thub par bshad la /
NK113(e)002:861: bye brag tu ni rang rang gi sngon las kyi
NK113(e)002:862: sgrib pa'i mthus byas pa'i phyir tshe'i tshad la nges
NK113(e)002:863: pa med par yang bshad do //
NK113(e)002:865: dud 'gro'am byol song gi skye gnas dag tu song
NK113(e)002:866: na yang rgya mtsho chen po'i nang du yod pa'i
NK113(e)002:867: byings gnas pa rnams ni phana tshun nya bo che
NK113(e)002:870: chu srin sogs che ba rnams kyis ni chung ba
NK113(e)002:871: mang po rgya mtsho'i chu dang lhan cig tu gyur
NK113(e)002:872: mid byed cing / chung ba mang pos che ba rnams kyi lus la tshang bca' ba dang /
NK113(e)002:873: thal mar 'bigs par byed pa'i sgo nas gcig la gciga bza' zhing /
NK113(e)002:874: kha 'thor ba la bdag tu ma bzung ba'i ri
NK113(e)002:875: dwags dang gcan gzan sogs ni rwa dang pags pa
NK113(e)002:876: sha la sogs pa'i phyir rngon byed pa'i gang zag
NK113(e)002:877: rnams kyi rgya dang go ra dug mda' la sogs
NK113(e)002:878: pa gsod pa'i las thabs kyis dam la bzhag ste
NK113(e)002:879: dbang du song nas sbyor ba rtsub mos srog 'phrog
NK113(e)002:880: par byed pa la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal dang /
NK113(e)002:881: mi la sogs pas bdag tu bzung ba rnams ni /
NK113(e)002:882: de dag gis bkola ba'i phyir rang gi lus 'dul
NK113(e)002:883: bar byed pa'i sga srab dang sna thag sogs rang
NK113(e)002:884: gis 'dzina dgos shing zhon nas 'gro ba dang /
NK113(e)002:887: thag ring por ded nas 'gro ba sogs kyi sdug bsngal gtad cing /
NK113(e)002:892: gsod par byed pa la sogs pa'i gnod pas rtag
NK113(e)002:893: tu mnar zhing rang dbang du r+ts+wa za ba dang
NK113(e)002:895: bag yangs su sdod pa'i skabs med pas nyam thag pa sogs dang /
NK113(e)002:896: spyi mthan du ni blun zhing rmongs pas thal mo ya gcig tsam yang sbyar mi shes /
NK113(e)002:897: ma ni rdog po gcig tsam yang 'don mi shes
NK113(e)002:898: pa de 'dra ba'i gnas su skye ba thob na
NK113(e)002:899: dam pa'i chos la thos bsam la sogs pa'i bya
NK113(e)002:900: ba ci zhig byar yoda de med do //
NK113(e)002:901: tshe tshad ni srin bu sogs kha cig yud tsam
NK113(e)002:902: nas klu la sogs pa kha cig bskal par gnas
NK113(e)002:904: bzhi pa 'du shes med pa'i lha ni /
NK113(e)002:905: srog 'tsho ba'i yun mi g.yo ba'i las mtha' shin
NK113(e)002:906: tu ring pos bsringsa te tshe yun ring por gnas
NK113(e)002:907: kyang / thar lam gyi rtsa ba 'khor bar skyo
NK113(e)002:908: ba'i nges 'byung gi sems skye ba'i go skabs mi
NK113(e)002:909: dbye ba'i gzugsa med pa dang zhes te bshes spring
NK113(e)002:910: gi 'grel par yang gzugs med par skyes pa'i so
NK113(e)002:911: skye rnams la thar lam bsgrub pa'i skal ba med
NK113(e)002:912: pas mi khom par bshad la /
NK113(e)002:913: mi khom pa brgyad kyi gtam las ni /
NK113(e)002:914: 'dod pa'i bya bas rtag tu g.yeng bas na 'dod pa'i lha rnams kyang mi khom par bshad do //
NK113(e)002:915: yang phyi rol 'ga' zhig thar pa'i lam du 'khrul
NK113(e)002:916: nas sems kun gzhi'i steng du tshogs drug gi shes
NK113(e)002:917: pa bkag nas bsgoms pa goms pas /
NK113(e)002:918: 'bras bu ni thos bsam gyi rten shes pa mngon
NK113(e)002:919: gyur 'aggas pa 'du shes med pa'i lhar skye ba
NK113(e)002:920: ste / lha de'i gnas ni bsam gtan bzhi pa'i
NK113(e)002:921: lha gnas 'bras bu che ba'i gnas na grong las
NK113(e)002:922: dgon pa'i tshul du yod par bshad do //
NK113(e)002:923: de las gzhan pa'i lha gnas rnams su ni nyan
NK113(e)002:924: rang 'phags pa rnams kyang skye ba 'dzin pas na
NK113(e)002:925: mi khom pa'i gnas min par yang gsungs so //
NK113(e)002:926: 'du shes med pa'i lha de 'du shes med pa'i
NK113(e)002:927: ngang du yun ring por gnas pa'i dus gron nas
NK113(e)002:928: 'chi khar rtog pa mngon gyur du ldang bas thar
NK113(e)002:929: ba'i lam med par 'dzin pa'i log par lta ba
NK113(e)002:930: skye bas ngan song du ltung ba'i phyir chos bsgrub
NK113(e)002:932: 'di dang 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug gi khyad par /
NK113(e)002:935: 'di la so so'i skye bo rnams 'jug cing 'phags pa rnams mi 'jug la /
NK113(e)002:936: 'gog bar 'phags pa rnams 'jug gi so so'i skye bo rnams 'jug mi nus so //
NK113(e)002:937: yang 'du shes med pa ni phyi rol pa rnams thar pa'i lam du 'khrul nas bsgom zhing /
NK113(e)002:938: 'gog pa la nyan rang 'phags pa rnams mthong chos bder gnas kyi phyir snyoms par 'jug la /
NK113(e)002:939: byang sems 'phags pa rnams ting nge 'dzin la rtsal sbyang ba'i phyir snyoms par 'jug go //
NK113(e)002:940: gnyis pa mir gyur pa'i mi khom pa bshad pa la bzhi ste /
NK113(e)002:944: mun pa'i bskal pa bstan pa'o //
NK113(e)002:946: rnam pa mi'i gzugs lta bu rkang pa gnyis po'i
NK113(e)002:947: khyogs la rab tu brten nas 'gro na yang chu
NK113(e)002:948: dang nags ma'i mi ltar ngo bo chos kyi phyogs
NK113(e)002:949: la shin tu rmongs pa dud 'gro lta bu la
NK113(e)002:950: de yi 'du shes ni bsod namas ma yin pa
NK113(e)002:951: mi dge bas dam la bazhaga cing dbang du byas
NK113(e)002:952: nas sdig pa'i las thabs bsgrub pa la gzhungsa pa
NK113(e)002:953: ste mkhas pa'i kla klo rnams dud 'gro las kyang
NK113(e)002:954: blang dor shin tu 'chol ba'i phyir nagsa tshal stug
NK113(e)002:955: po'i nang na 'khyamsa te lam mi shes pa ltar
NK113(e)002:957: yang na 'di dag yod pa'i gnas phal cher nags
NK113(e)002:958: tshal yin pas de skad ces bya ste 'du shes
NK113(e)002:959: mi khom pa'o // gnyis pa lkugs pa ni /
NK113(e)002:960: 'dir rab brtags kyi rgyan du bkod de mig nas
NK113(e)002:961: yid kyi bar dabnga po drug po so so'i mig
NK113(e)002:962: gis gzugs la blta ba la sogs pa rang rang
NK113(e)002:963: gi dam bca' byasa pa de nyamsa pa'i ngag rang
NK113(e)002:964: gi bya ba smra mi shes pa dang /
NK113(e)002:965: khyad par du yid shin tu blun pa'i lkugsa par gyur pa rnams ni /
NK113(e)002:966: 'aphagas pa'i sa la gnas pa'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen
NK113(e)002:967: la sogs pa gdul bya thar par 'dren pa'i ded
NK113(e)002:968: dpona dag dang phrad nas chos thos par gyur kyang
NK113(e)002:969: nyan pa po rang gi dbang po nyams pa'i skyon
NK113(e)002:970: gyis 'chad pa pos smras pa'i tshig de yang braga
NK113(e)002:971: cha'i cho ga ste bya bas bzung ba'i ca co'i
NK113(e)002:973: tshig la brten nas don nyan pa po de la
NK113(e)002:974: brda mi 'phroda pa'i phyir blang dor gyi gnas nyams
NK113(e)002:975: su len pa'i skal pa chad nas 'khor ba'i gnas
NK113(e)002:976: 'broga dgon pa chen po lta bu 'jigs su rung
NK113(e)002:977: ba 'dir sdug bsngal sna tshogs kyis yun ring po
NK113(e)002:978: gdungsa shing mnar bar 'gyur ba las thar pa mya
NK113(e)002:979: ngan las 'das pa'i go 'phang thob pa'i skal ba
NK113(e)002:980: med pas rten mi khom pa'o //
NK113(e)002:981: gsum pa log lta can ni /
NK113(e)002:982: las dang nyon mongs pa'i dbang gis 'khor bar skye
NK113(e)002:983: ba'i rang bzhin gting mtha' thugs pa med pa'i rgya
NK113(e)002:984: mtsho chen po lta bu 'di brgal nas thar pa'i
NK113(e)002:985: gling du bgrod pa'i gru bo che mi yi lus
NK113(e)002:986: rten thob cing dbang po tshang la rnam rig cang
NK113(e)002:987: shes pa'i ba dan thar pa'i phyogs su g.yo rung
NK113(e)002:988: ba thob nas kyang bslar yang rten bzang chud gzon
NK113(e)002:989: pa'i lta ba ma rungs pas rgyud dkrugs te sangsa
NK113(e)002:990: rgyas 'jig rten du 'byung zhing yang dag pa'i chos
NK113(e)002:991: bstan pa la zhugs nas thugs mnyes pa'i thabs rnam
NK113(e)002:992: par grol ba'i lam bsgrub par mi bgyid cing /
NK113(e)002:993: 'jig rten pha rol med do zhes pa la sogs
NK113(e)002:994: pa'i loga par lta ba 'dzin pa'i mu stegs can
NK113(e)002:995: nam de'i phyogs su gtogs pa mchog gsum la yid
NK113(e)002:996: mi ches pa'i gang zag de ni thar lam la
NK113(e)002:997: bar du gcod pa'i bdud kyis gtsesa te dbang du
NK113(e)002:998: song ba yin pas lus rten bzang yang yid mi
NK113(e)002:999: khom pa'o // bzhi pa mun pa'i bskal pa ni /
NK113(e)002:1000: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byon pa de'i tshe bstan
NK113(e)002:1001: pa'i snang ba'ang yod pas sgron me'i bskal pa zhes
NK113(e)002:1002: bya la / bskal pa gang zhig chags nas zhig
NK113(e)002:1003: gi bar thub pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams
NK113(e)002:1004: kyis spangsa pa ste sangs rgyas gcig kyang ma byon
NK113(e)002:1005: pa'i dus de la bstan pa'i snang ba'ang med pas
NK113(e)002:1006: mun pa'i bskal pa zhes bya ste de yi skabs
NK113(e)002:1007: su mi'i lus rten thob kyang phan pa med de
NK113(e)002:1008: bya la / / dper na skyes bu rkang pa
NK113(e)002:1009: chag pa zhig gcong rong zab mo mun nag 'thibas
NK113(e)002:1010: po 'khrigs par gyur pa'i nang du ltung bar gyur
NK113(e)002:1011: bya la / / na / de slar yang ldang
NK113(e)002:1012: bar brtson kyang lam mi mthong zhing bgrod byed kyi
NK113(e)002:1013: rkang pa med pas ma thar ba ltar /
NK113(e)002:1014: rnam par grol ba'i lam gyi snang ba yod pa
NK113(e)002:1015: min zhing thar bar bgrod byed kyi bslab gsum dang
NK113(e)002:1016: bral nas ma rig pa dang nyon mongs pas bskyed
NK113(e)002:1017: pa'i phyin ci log gi lam rgyun chags su ldan
NK113(e)002:1018: pas de ni nyam nga ba'i gnas su ltung bas
NK113(e)002:1019: thar bar mi 'gyur bar ma zad dud 'gro nas
NK113(e)002:1020: dmyal ba'i bar 'og nas 'og tu 'gro bar 'gyur
NK113(e)002:1021: ba ste / de ni 'gro ba mu bzhi las
NK113(e)002:1022: mun pa nas mun par 'gro ba yin pas dus
NK113(e)002:1023: ba ste / mi khom pa'o // gzhan yang yid bzhin rin po cher /
NK113(e)002:1024: dug lnga 'khrugs dang blun rmongs bdud kyis zin //
NK113(e)002:1025: le lo can dang las ngan mtsho chen rdol //
NK113(e)002:1026: gzhan dbang 'jigs skyob chos ltar bcos pa ste //
NK113(e)002:1027: 'phral byung rkyen gyi mi khom rnam pa brgyad //
NK113(e)002:1028: thar lam chos kyi snod min phyin ci log /
NK113(e)002:1030: 'ching ba dam ldan kun spyod shin tu ngan //
NK113(e)002:1031: 'khor bar mi skyo dad pa cung zad med //
NK113(e)002:1032: mi dge sdig spyod chos la sems pa bral //
NK113(e)002:1033: sdom dang dam tshig nyams pa zhes bya ba //
NK113(e)002:1034: ris chad blo yi mi khom rnam pa brgyad //
NK113(e)002:1035: chos las ring gyur thar lam sgron me nub //
NK113(e)002:1036: ces gsungs pa'i brgyad tshan gnyis po 'di dag la
NK113(e)002:1037: yang dpyad pa legs par zhugs nas blang dor ma
NK113(e)002:1038: byas na mir gyur nas sos dal ba tsam ni
NK113(e)002:1039: chos sgrub pa'i rten du rung daka'o //
NK113(e)002:1040: gsum pa mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK113(e)002:1041: rgyu sdig pa mi dge ba dang 'bras bu sdug
NK113(e)002:1042: bsngal sna tshogs pa bskal pa 'thor byed kyi rlung
NK113(e)002:1043: 'khrugsa pa lta bu'i gnas rigsa rnams su lus ngal
NK113(e)002:1044: zhing sems skrag pa dang bacasa pa'i rang bzhin ni
NK113(e)002:1045: bsod nams rnyog pa mi dge ba'i ngang tshul can
NK113(e)002:1046: dam pa'i chos la phrag pa dog pa ste bsgrub
NK113(e)002:1047: pa'i go skabs med pa'i mi khom pa'i gnas brgyad
NK113(e)002:1048: po dag tu da lta ma skyes pa'i tshul la
NK113(e)002:1049: yang yang bsam nas bla ma dang man ngag zab
NK113(e)002:1050: mo la bsten te rang gi blo bcos su yod
NK113(e)002:1051: pa'i skabs 'dir dal ba thob pa don yod par
NK113(e)002:1052: bya ba'i phyir thar pa'i lam rnam par dag pa
NK113(e)002:1053: bsgrub par mdzoda cig ces gdams pa'o //
NK113(e)002:1054: khyad par bla na med pa theg pa chen po'i dal 'byor ni /
NK113(e)002:1055: nam mkha' rin po che mdo las /
NK113(e)002:1056: bcom ldan 'das dal 'byor ji ltar blta bar bgyi /
NK113(e)002:1058: sems rnam par rtog pas dbyen bcos te g.yeng ba ni brel ba zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:1059: sems rnam par rtog pa zhi nas rang bzhin du gnas pa ni dal ba zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:1060: 'byor pa ni sems kyi rang bzhin shes pa /
NK113(e)002:1061: blo yang dag pa'i don la 'byor bas na 'byor ba zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:1063: gsum pa dal 'byor gyi rang bzhin ngos gzung ba la gsum ste /
NK113(e)002:1066: gnyis ka bsdoms te bstan pa'o //
NK113(e)002:1068: spyir sa tshigs kyi yul dbus 'phags yul gyi rdo
NK113(e)002:1069: rje'i gdan yin pas sngon dus sa tshigs dang chos
NK113(e)002:1070: tshigs gnyis ka'i yul dbus rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul
NK113(e)002:1071: yin la / bod 'dir bstan pa ma dar gong
NK113(e)002:1072: du mtha' 'khob yin kyang da lta lung dang rtog
NK113(e)002:1073: pa'i bstan pa dar zhing gnas pa'i phyir chos tshigs
NK113(e)002:1074: kyi yul dbus yin pas sa gzhi gtsang ma dang
NK113(e)002:1076: yal ga dang lo ma lta bu thos bsam dang
NK113(e)002:1077: bslab pa'i rten dbang po sgo lnga dang yan lag
NK113(e)002:1078: dang nying lag thams cad rab tu tshang zhing rdzogsa
NK113(e)002:1079: pa dang / dad pa'i gnas rgyal ba'i bstan pa la dad pa thob pa dang /
NK113(e)002:1080: sgo gsum gyi las matha'i me tog mtshams med dang /
NK113(e)002:1081: rtag tu chos dang 'gal ba'i sdig to mi dge
NK113(e)002:1082: ba byed pa dang dkon mchog la blo gtad log
NK113(e)002:1083: pa la sogs pas ma bcom pa'i phyir las mtha'
NK113(e)002:1085: de dag tshang ba'i mi lus ni 'gro ba drug
NK113(e)002:1086: gi nang nas lha chos kyi rten mi yi lus
NK113(e)002:1087: khyad par can du gyur pas na 'di ni rnam
NK113(e)002:1088: par grol ba'i yon tan thams cad yid la ji
NK113(e)002:1089: ltar 'dod pa bzhin thob pa'i rten yin pas dapaga
NK113(e)002:1090: bsam gyi ljon pa dang 'dra bar shin tu rnyed
NK113(e)002:1091: pa dkona zhing don che bas rang rgyud rten gyi
NK113(e)002:1092: 'byor pa ste lnga po tshang ba 'di la snying
NK113(e)002:1093: po lon pa zhig nges par gces so //
NK113(e)002:1094: gnyis pa gzhan 'byor lnga bshad pa ni /
NK113(e)002:1095: rtog pa brjod pa'i mdo las /
NK113(e)002:1096: mtsho chen po ma dros pa 'das pa'i byang phyogs
NK113(e)002:1097: na ri rtse lnga pa zhes bya ba de'i pha
NK113(e)002:1098: rol na u dum w+aa ra'i tshal yod de nam
NK113(e)002:1099: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das dag dga' ldan gyi lha'i
NK113(e)002:1100: gnas ris nas babs te yum gyi lhums su zhugs
NK113(e)002:1101: pa de'i tshe tshal de kha 'bus bar 'gyur ro
NK113(e)002:1102: // nam yum gyi lhums nas bltams pa de'i tshe tshal de kha bye bar gyur ro //
NK113(e)002:1104: nam yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa de'i tshe
NK113(e)002:1105: tshal de'i me tog dang 'dab ma dang 'bras bu
NK113(e)002:1108: rgyal ba bcom ldan 'das 'byung dka' ba u dum
NK113(e)002:1109: w+aa ra lta bu bdag cag gi ston pa mi
NK113(e)002:1110: mjed 'jiga rten gyi khams 'dir byon pa dang /
NK113(e)002:1111: chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum gyi me tog
NK113(e)002:1112: kha bye ste gdul bya'i blo dang 'tshams par gsungs
NK113(e)002:1113: pa dang / lung dang rtogs pa'i bstan pa'i tshal
NK113(e)002:1114: de bshad pa dang sgrub pa'i sgo nas nub pa
NK113(e)002:1115: med par da lta yang gnas pa dang /
NK113(e)002:1116: bstan pa de la yang dag par zhugs pa'i thar
NK113(e)002:1117: pa'i lam mkhan dge ba'i bshes gnyen yod pa dang
NK113(e)002:1118: / dam pa de'i thugs rje'i grib bsil la brten
NK113(e)002:1119: du yod pa ste gzhan rkyen gyi 'byor pa lnga
NK113(e)002:1120: ni rang 'byor pa lnga ni rang 'byor lnga po
NK113(e)002:1121: de bas kyang nyung bas mthun rkyen de dag tshang
NK113(e)002:1122: ba'i dus 'dir tshe 'di'i rnam par g.yengs ba thams
NK113(e)002:1123: cad spangs nas le lo dang phyi bshol med par
NK113(e)002:1124: skyes bu dam pa rnams kyi rjes su bsnyegs te
NK113(e)002:1125: lung dang rtogs pa'i chos mdzod 'dzin nus pa zhig
NK113(e)002:1126: nges par bya'o snyam du bsam mo //
NK113(e)002:1127: gsum pa gnyis ka bsdoms te bstan pa ni /
NK113(e)002:1128: myur du lam la brtson dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan gang gi phyir yin zhe na /
NK113(e)002:1129: rang nyid kyi 'byor pa'i yon tan dpag bsam gyi ljon pa tsam du dkon pa dang /
NK113(e)002:1130: gzhan dbang rkyen gyis 'byor pa'i yon tan de bas
NK113(e)002:1131: kyang dkon pa u dum w+aa ra'i me tog dang
NK113(e)002:1132: 'dra bar gyur pa de gnyis ka'i yon tan zung
NK113(e)002:1133: du tshogs pa'i khyad chos 'byor pa rnam pa bcus
NK113(e)002:1134: khyad gzhi dal ba brgyad la 'khyud pa ste ldan
NK113(e)002:1135: pa 'di la ni mi lus rin po che zhes
NK113(e)002:1136: brjod du rung bas da lta snying po lon par
NK113(e)002:1137: ma byas na slar 'di lta bu mi rnyed do
NK113(e)002:1138: // bzhi pa rnyed par dka' ba'i rgyu mtshan bshad pa ni /
NK113(e)002:1139: rnyed dka' ba'i rgyu mtshan ci yi phyir zhe na /
NK113(e)002:1141: stong gsum rgya mtsho gcig tu gyur pa'i gting na
NK113(e)002:1142: rus sbal long ba lo brgya re'i mtshams su lan
NK113(e)002:1143: re mtsho khar 'ong ba zhig yod na de'i mgrin
NK113(e)002:1144: pa dang mtsho khar rlung gis bdas pa'i gnya' shing
NK113(e)002:1145: bu ga gcig pa zhig yod na de gnyis 'phrad
NK113(e)002:1146: pa bas mi'i skye ba thob pa dka' bar gsungs
NK113(e)002:1147: pa sogs dpe'i sgo nas rnyed dka' bar bstan to
NK113(e)002:1148: // de tsam thob dka' na mi lus mang po
NK113(e)002:1149: 'di tsam du yod pa ci yin snyam na 'gro
NK113(e)002:1150: ba gzhan gyi grangs la bsam na ni mi lus
NK113(e)002:1152: da lta mi mang po yod pa ltar snang ba
NK113(e)002:1153: 'di dang dud 'gro gnyis kyi grangs bsdur na mi
NK113(e)002:1154: rnams la nyin mo'i skar ma tsam la /
NK113(e)002:1155: dud 'gro la mtshan mo'i skar ma tsam ste /
NK113(e)002:1156: tshul 'di mngon sum du mthong bas kyang shes te /
NK113(e)002:1160: nyi zer gcig la mthong ba'i srog chags la ltos
NK113(e)002:1161: na mi lus ni 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po
NK113(e)002:1163: mi rnams la bsam na yang tshong 'dus lta bu'i
NK113(e)002:1164: tshogs pa mang po'i khrod na chos ldan gyi mi
NK113(e)002:1165: lus ni sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byon pa las
NK113(e)002:1166: dkon pa'i tshul la bsam te rang la rang gis
NK113(e)002:1167: spro ba bskyed de dal 'byor chud ma zos pa'i
NK113(e)002:1169: mi dang dud 'gro la nyin mtshan gyi skar ma'i
NK113(e)002:1170: grangs kyis phye ba de snyed kyis dud 'gro dang
NK113(e)002:1171: yi dwagsa / yi dwags dang dmyal ba rnams la dpag na rima pas shes par 'gyur la /
NK113(e)002:1172: gzhan yang dmyal ba na sa chen po'i rdul tsam /
NK113(e)002:1173: yi dwags la gad+g+aa'i klung gi bye ma tsam /
NK113(e)002:1174: dud 'gro la chang ngar ma'i sbang ma tsam yod pa la /
NK113(e)002:1175: lha mi gnyis ni de dag la ltos na sen
NK113(e)002:1176: mo'i steng gi rdul tsam las med par gsungs so
NK113(e)002:1178: dge slong dag ngan song ba'i 'gro ba la ltos
NK113(e)002:1179: na phyi phyir mi nyid kyi dngos po thob pa
NK113(e)002:1181: zhes gsungs pa la sogs pa'i tshul la bsam nas
NK113(e)002:1182: 'jig rten gyi rnam par g.yengs pa thams cad spangs
NK113(e)002:1183: nas bslab pa gsum gyi yon tan tshul bzhin rgyud
NK113(e)002:1185: lnga pa gdams ngag brjod pas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK113(e)002:1187: mi yi gru la brten nas ni //
NK113(e)002:1188: sdug bsngal chu bo che las sgrol //
NK113(e)002:1189: gru 'di phyi nas rnyed dka' bas //
NK113(e)002:1190: rmongs pa dus su gnyid ma log /
NK113(e)002:1192: rnyed dka' zhing don che ba de yi phyir rten
NK113(e)002:1193: dal ba dang 'byor pa'i rang bzhin brten pa rnam
NK113(e)002:1194: par shes pa las su rung ba dang lhan cig
NK113(e)002:1195: tshogs pa'i lus rten gru chen po rang dbang du
NK113(e)002:1196: 'dzin pa'i skabs thob pa 'di ni lha bas kyang
NK113(e)002:1197: lhag ste lha rnams gnas rigs la nga rgyal du
NK113(e)002:1198: byed pas bden pa mngon par rtogs dka' la theg
NK113(e)002:1199: pa che chung gi rten khyad par ba ni 'dzam
NK113(e)002:1200: gling gi mi kho na yin pas so //
NK113(e)002:1201: des na da res kyi dus su 'khor ba'i rang
NK113(e)002:1202: bzhin sdug bsngal mtha' yangs la gting zab pa chu
NK113(e)002:1203: gter lta bu'i pha mtha' thar pa'i skam sar ma
NK113(e)002:1204: brgal na chos kyi lam du zhugs pa'i mgron pos
NK113(e)002:1205: rnam grol don du gnyera zhing thob pa'i skabas btsal
NK113(e)002:1206: ba'i tshe 'dren pa'i ded dpon gyi bla ma dam
NK113(e)002:1207: pa gzings kyi kha lo sgyur ba'i mnyan pa dang
NK113(e)002:1208: 'dra bar 'phrad pa 'di 'bras bu med par bgyid
NK113(e)002:1209: pa la mngon par phyogsa pa yin pa'i tshul la
NK113(e)002:1212: 'di la gcig tu bsam par bya ba ni dal
NK113(e)002:1213: ba ste spro bas rjes su dran par gyis shig
NK113(e)002:1215: yon tan rin po che'i mdzoda dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba lasa /
NK113(e)002:1216: dal 'byor gyi rnam para dbye ba'i tshoms te /
NK113(e)002:1217: tshoms zhes pa ni gzhung skor tshoms su bcad pa'i don no //
NK113(e)002:1218: la'u ni pa rits+tshe ta'i sgra las yongs su bcad
NK113(e)002:1219: pa'am dum bur byas pa la 'jug pas 'dir yang
NK113(e)002:1220: de yin la / dang po ni le'u rnams kyi
NK113(e)002:1221: thog ma smos pa'i sgra ste gral gyi mgo na
NK113(e)002:1223: 'o zhes pa ni skabs de rdzogs pa'i don no //
NK113(e)002:1224: 'dir de nyid 'grel pa la spyir 'grel tshul drug ste /
NK113(e)002:1231: dang po'i dbang du byas pa yin no ////
NK113(e)002:1232: don gnyis pa brtson 'grus kyi lcag 'debs pa tshe mi rtag pa bsgom pa'i le'u la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:1233: spyir snod dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten la bsam nas mi rtag pa bsgom pa /
NK113(e)002:1234: bye brag bcud kyi 'gro ba la bsam nas mi rtag pa bsgom pa'o //
NK113(e)002:1239: snod bcud kyi 'jig rten la chags gnas 'jig stongs bzhi las /
NK113(e)002:1240: dang po chags pa la snod bcud gnyis las /
NK113(e)002:1241: dang po snod ni nam mkha' la brten pa rnams yas nas chags shing /
NK113(e)002:1242: sa gzhi la brten pa rnams ni mas nas chags te /
NK113(e)002:1243: de'i tshul ni dang po rten gzhi 'byung ba'i dkyil
NK113(e)002:1244: 'khor chags te 'di ltar nam mkha'i rang bzhin stong
NK113(e)002:1245: la go 'byed pa'i klong du rnam par bsrubs byed
NK113(e)002:1246: dang / kun tu khyab byed dang /
NK113(e)002:1250: 'byed byed de rlung drug gi byed las stobs su
NK113(e)002:1251: gyur nas rlung gi rdo rje rgya gram gang gis
NK113(e)002:1252: kyang mi gzhig pa'i steng du gser gyi snying po
NK113(e)002:1253: can gyi sprin las char babs pas chu'i dkyil 'khor
NK113(e)002:1254: rten byed rlung gi mu khyud can chags shing /
NK113(e)002:1255: de nas rnam par bsrubs byed kyi rlung gis chu
NK113(e)002:1256: de bsrubs pa las dbang chen gser gyi sa gzhi
NK113(e)002:1257: chags so // de'i steng du rten ri gling mtsho
NK113(e)002:1258: rnams chags te de yang chu dang sa bsrubs shing
NK113(e)002:1259: khams sna tshogs can gyi sprin las char babs pas
NK113(e)002:1260: dbus su ri rgyal lhun po rin chen bzhi las
NK113(e)002:1261: grub pa'i phyi rol du gser ri bdun gyis phyi
NK113(e)002:1262: nang gi rim pas bskor ba'i bar rnams rol mtsho
NK113(e)002:1263: bdun gyis gang zhing gser ri phyi ma dang matha'i
NK113(e)002:1264: lcags ri'i bar ba tsh+wa can gyi chus gang ba'i
NK113(e)002:1265: phyogs bzhi dang mtshams rnams su chu dang kha mnyam
NK113(e)002:1266: pa las cung zad mtho ba'i rnam pas gling bzhi
NK113(e)002:1267: gling phran brgyad po bcas chags so //
NK113(e)002:1268: ngan song gi gnas ni ti se'i 'og nas dpag
NK113(e)002:1269: tshad nyi khri nas rim bzhin tshad dmyal brgyad po
NK113(e)002:1271: de'i byang da ngos su dpag tshad nyi shu na
NK113(e)002:1272: de dang 'dab 'byor du grang dmyal brgyad po'i gnas
NK113(e)002:1273: yod la / nyi tshe ba'i gnas la nges pa
NK113(e)002:1274: med cing nye 'khor ba ni tsha dmyal gyi 'khor
NK113(e)002:1275: yod la / du gnas so // yi dwags ni
NK113(e)002:1276: rgyal po'i khab kyi 'og dpag tshad lnga brgya na
NK113(e)002:1277: rtsa ba'i gnas yod cing yan lag lha mi'i gnas
NK113(e)002:1278: yod la / du gnas so // na'ang yod do
NK113(e)002:1279: // dud 'gro byings gnas rgya mtsho chen po dang
NK113(e)002:1280: kha 'thor lha dang mi'i yul na gnas so //
NK113(e)002:1281: 'dod pa'i lha'i gnas sa la brten pa ni gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:1282: rgyal chen ris bzhi ri rab kyi bang rim bzhi dang /
NK113(e)002:1284: skar ma'i gzhal med khang dang gser ri dang khor yug gi rtse mo sogs na yod la /
NK113(e)002:1285: sum cu rtsa gsum pa'i gnas ni lhun po'i steng ngo //
NK113(e)002:1286: nam mkha' la brten pa'i 'dod lha'i gnas bzhi ni
NK113(e)002:1287: ri rab kyi steng gi nam mkhar gong nas gong
NK113(e)002:1289: lha ma yin gyi gnas ri rab kyi chu mtshams
NK113(e)002:1290: man chad nas gser gyi sa gzhi'i bar khong seng
NK113(e)002:1292: de'i sde tshan du gtogs pa 'gang zhig mi la sogs pa'i gnas na'ang yod do //
NK113(e)002:1293: gzugs khams la gnas ris bco brgyad las 'dod lha
NK113(e)002:1294: gong ma'i steng gi nam mkha' nas rim bzhin so
NK113(e)002:1296: de'i steng 'phags pa'i gnas gtsang ris lnga ste gnas
NK113(e)002:1297: 'di dag na gzhung 'ga' zhig tu so skye yang
NK113(e)002:1298: yod par gsungs shing de ltar na thog mar srid
NK113(e)002:1299: pa mched tshul srid pa'i rtse mo nas yin pas
NK113(e)002:1301: de'i gong na byang sems srid pa tha ma ba'i
NK113(e)002:1302: gnas 'og min rnam mdzes zhes bya ba yod do
NK113(e)002:1303: // gzugs med pa la dngos snang gi gnas rags phra gang yang med do //
NK113(e)002:1304: de ltar chags pa'i gling bzhi ri rab 'dod lha
NK113(e)002:1305: tshangs pa'i 'jig rten dang bcas pa la gling bzhi
NK113(e)002:1306: pa'i 'jig rten gyi khams zhes bya zhing /
NK113(e)002:1307: de stong la spyi phud stong gi 'jig rten dang /
NK113(e)002:1308: de stong la bar ma'i 'jig rten dang /
NK113(e)002:1309: de stong la stong gsum gyi stong chen po zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:1310: gnyis pa brten pa bcud kyi sems can chags tshul ni /
NK113(e)002:1311: yas nas rim pa bzhin du ste /
NK113(e)002:1312: bdud rtsi'i char babs pas sa las rlung 'byung rin
NK113(e)002:1313: po che'i shing sna tshogs pad+ma'i rang bzhin du smin
NK113(e)002:1314: par byas pas thog ma'i snod kyi rten gzhi'i 'byung
NK113(e)002:1315: ba bzhi chags pa'i dus so so'i 'dab 'byor du
NK113(e)002:1316: byung ba'i srid pa'i sems can rlung gi lha mo
NK113(e)002:1317: bzhi dang chu'i lha mo gar byed pa mang po
NK113(e)002:1318: / sa'i lha mo bzhi dang klu'i bu stobs ldan
NK113(e)002:1319: bzhi rnams kyi yid zhugs pa dang bcas pa'i sgras
NK113(e)002:1320: srid rtse'i gzugs med smin rung gi rnam shes bag
NK113(e)002:1321: la nyal mngon gyur du sad pa'i rkyen byed par
NK113(e)002:1322: bshad pa ni srid pa chags tshul rang sa'i grub
NK113(e)002:1323: / mtha' ste / gzhan du na dbyings kyi rig
NK113(e)002:1324: pa lung ma bstan g.yos pa las sems can glo
NK113(e)002:1325: bur ba'i 'khrul pa ni ma nges te /
NK113(e)002:1327: e ma ho bde gshegs snying po las //
NK113(e)002:1328: rang rang rnam rtog las kyis sprul //
NK113(e)002:1330: de'i phyir gzugs med rnams ni thog ma'i gzhi las
NK113(e)002:1331: 'khrul te ma rig pas bsdus pa'i bsam gtan bzhir
NK113(e)002:1332: gol bas gong nas 'og mar mched de stong rig
NK113(e)002:1333: ting 'dzin gyi lus tsam zhig rim pas nam mkha'
NK113(e)002:1335: gzugs khams pa ni 'od kyi lus la sems kyi
NK113(e)002:1336: rgyun brten nas ting nge 'dzin gyi dga' bas yun
NK113(e)002:1337: ring du gnas te rin po che so so'i kha
NK113(e)002:1338: dog dang mthun pas de dang de'i ming gis btags
NK113(e)002:1339: pa'i nam mkha' la rim pas nam mkha' mtha' yas
NK113(e)002:1340: kyi 'og nas gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi steng gi
NK113(e)002:1341: nam mkha'i bar du mched cing chags so //
NK113(e)002:1342: de las mched pa'i 'dod pa'i lha rnams ni so
NK113(e)002:1343: so'i longs spyod kyis brgyan pa'i ming gis btags pa'i
NK113(e)002:1344: nam mkhar gnas pa bzhi dang /
NK113(e)002:1345: gtso bo'i ming gis btags pa'i sa gzhi la brten
NK113(e)002:1346: pa gnyis te drug tu chags shing lha min rnams
NK113(e)002:1347: lha'i rigs ma rung pa 'ga' las chad de sngar
NK113(e)002:1348: bshad pa ltar ri rab kyi khong seng du chags
NK113(e)002:1349: so // mi rnams las 'dzam bu'i gling pa rnams
NK113(e)002:1350: ni 'od gsal gyi lha nas bsod nams chung ngu
NK113(e)002:1351: zhig gling 'dir 'ong nas rim par mched de /
NK113(e)002:1352: de'i dus su rdzu 'phrul gyis mkha' la 'gro zhing
NK113(e)002:1353: lus 'od dang bcas la dga' bde'i zas kyis 'tsho
NK113(e)002:1354: zhing tshe lo dpag tu med pa thub cing nyon
NK113(e)002:1355: mongs mngon gyur med la rdzus te skye ba sha
NK113(e)002:1356: stag go // de nas ring zhig na mi zhes
NK113(e)002:1357: grags tshun chad nas tshe dang 'od bri zhing bsod
NK113(e)002:1358: nams chung dur song ste nyon mongs bag nyal langs
NK113(e)002:1359: shing mngon gyur langs su nye ba na /
NK113(e)002:1360: gong ma'i lha las lus 'phags dang ba lang spyod pa rnams dang /
NK113(e)002:1361: sum cu rtsa gsum las sgra mi snyan pa rnams
NK113(e)002:1362: rang rang gi gling phran dang bcas rim gyis chags
NK113(e)002:1363: so // de nas 'dzam gling gi mi rnams dga'
NK113(e)002:1364: bdes g.yeng bar gyur nas lo bye ba dag na
NK113(e)002:1365: sgo nga las skye ba dang /
NK113(e)002:1366: lo sa ya drug 'bum na drod gsher skye dang /
NK113(e)002:1367: de las 'od bri zhing gti mug gi dbang gis mun pa byung ba'i tshe /
NK113(e)002:1368: spyi mthun gyi las las nyi zla gza' skar sogs
NK113(e)002:1369: byung ste dus tshigs kyang yod par 'gyur zhing pho
NK113(e)002:1370: mo'i dbang po'ang dod par gyur te de yan chad
NK113(e)002:1372: de nas mi rigs bzhi yang byung zhing dug gsum
NK113(e)002:1373: gyi dbang gis las sna tshogs tshabs cher bsags par
NK113(e)002:1374: gyur to // ngan song gi 'gro ba ni mi
NK113(e)002:1375: rnams la nyon mongs mngon gyur langs pa'i dbang gis
NK113(e)002:1376: dug gsum gyi las kyis byung ste /
NK113(e)002:1377: de ltar dmyal ba'i gnas su sems can gcig skyes
NK113(e)002:1378: pa na chags pa'i bskal pa rdzogs pa yin te
NK113(e)002:1379: / snod chags pa la bar bskal gcig dang /
NK113(e)002:1380: bcud chags pa la bcu dgu ste nyi shu'o //
NK113(e)002:1381: gnyis pa ji ltar gnas pa'i tshul ni /
NK113(e)002:1382: tshe lo dpag med nas brgyad khri'i bar lo nyis brgya re'i mtshams su lo re bri zhing /
NK113(e)002:1383: brgyad khri nas bcu pa'i bar brgya re'i mtshams su
NK113(e)002:1384: re re bri ba ste bcu pa rdzogs nas yar
NK113(e)002:1385: 'phel ba'i 'go ma brtsams yan chad la ya thog
NK113(e)002:1386: ring mo 'grib pa'i bskal pa zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:1387: dee nas bcu pa nas yar brgya brgya na sde
NK113(e)002:1388: tshan bcu gnyis kyi rim pas nyi shu dang bzhi
NK113(e)002:1389: bcu dang brgya dang nyis brgya dang lnga brgya dang
NK113(e)002:1390: stong dang nyis stong dang lnga stong dang khri dang
NK113(e)002:1391: nyi khri dang bzhi khri dang brgyad khri'i bar 'phel
NK113(e)002:1392: zhing / tshul de lta bus brgyad khri nas bcu
NK113(e)002:1393: pa'i bar mar 'grib pa la bar gyi khug pa
NK113(e)002:1394: zhing / zhes bya ste / de 'dra ba bco
NK113(e)002:1395: brgyad song rjes su sde tshan gyis dpag med par
NK113(e)002:1396: zhing / zhes bya ste / yar 'phel zhing /
NK113(e)002:1397: ya thog ltar dal gyis bcu pa'i bar 'grib pa
NK113(e)002:1398: la ma thog ring mo 'phel 'grib kyi bskal pa
NK113(e)002:1399: zhing / zhes bya ste / yar 'phel zhing /
NK113(e)002:1400: zhes bya'o // de ltar ya thog dang bar khug
NK113(e)002:1401: dang ma thog dang bcas pa la rnam grangs kyi
NK113(e)002:1402: bar bskal nyi shu ste gnas pa'i dus so //
NK113(e)002:1403: de dag gi tshe mar 'grib kyi dus su bar
NK113(e)002:1404: gyi sangs rgyas gsum dang bskal bzang gi sangs rgyas
NK113(e)002:1406: dpag med nas brgyad khri'i bar 'khor los sgyur ba'ang mang du 'byung la /
NK113(e)002:1407: rang sangs rgyas ni yar skye mar 'grib gnyis kar 'byung ba yin no //
NK113(e)002:1408: gsum pa 'jig pa'i tshu la gnyis las /
NK113(e)002:1409: dang po bcud kyi sems can ni gnas bskal nyi
NK113(e)002:1410: shu pa rdzogs nas dmyal ba'i 'jig rten du sems
NK113(e)002:1411: can gser du skye bar mi 'gyur ba nas 'jig
NK113(e)002:1412: pa'i mgo 'dzin zhing der skyes zin pa rnams mtho
NK113(e)002:1413: ris su 'gro ba la las ma zad pa rnams
NK113(e)002:1414: ni 'jig rten gyi khams gzhan gyi dmyal bar skye'o
NK113(e)002:1415: // ngan song gzhan gnyis kyang tshul de dang 'dra'o //
NK113(e)002:1416: mi rnams las sgra mi snyan pa rnams sum cu
NK113(e)002:1417: rtsa gsum du skye bar 'gyur zhing gzhan gsum mtshungs
NK113(e)002:1418: par bsam gtan gnyis pa'i sems thob nas 'od gsal
NK113(e)002:1419: du skye'o // 'dod pa'i lha rnams dang bsam gtan
NK113(e)002:1420: dang po'i gnas na gnas pa'i lha rnams kyang tshul
NK113(e)002:1421: du skye'o // de dang 'dra'o // chus 'jig gi
NK113(e)002:1422: tshe bsam gtan gnyis pa ba rnams gsum par dang
NK113(e)002:1424: gi tshe bsam gtan gsum pa ba rnams bzhi po'i
NK113(e)002:1425: sems thob nas der skye ba ste de'i tshe gnas
NK113(e)002:1426: de rnams na sems can gcig kyang med par 'gyur
NK113(e)002:1428: gnyis pa snod kyi 'jig rten 'jug pa'i tshul ni
NK113(e)002:1430: / nyi ma bdun gyis te dang pos rtsi shing
NK113(e)002:1431: nags tshal thams cad bsregs pa nas bdun pas ri
NK113(e)002:1432: gling gser gyi sa gzhi'i bar thams cad bsregs shing
NK113(e)002:1433: me lce gyen du bskyod pas bsam gtan dang po'i
NK113(e)002:1434: gzhal med khang stong pa thams cad lhag ma ma
NK113(e)002:1435: lus par bsregs par byed do //
NK113(e)002:1436: de ltar mes lan bdun bsreg pa'i rjes su nam
NK113(e)002:1437: mkha' las char babs pas bams gtan gnyis pa man
NK113(e)002:1438: chad lan tsh+wa chur zhu ba ltar zhig par 'gyur
NK113(e)002:1439: ro // de ltar zhig pa'i rjes su bsam gtan
NK113(e)002:1440: gsum pa man chad rlung gis gtor te stongs par
NK113(e)002:1441: ro // 'gyur ro // de yang bsam gtan dang po na rtog dpyod me dang 'dra ba dang /
NK113(e)002:1442: gnyis pa na dga' bde'i rlan chu dang 'dra ba dang /
NK113(e)002:1443: gsum pa na dbugs kyi 'byung rdub rlung dang 'dra
NK113(e)002:1444: ba rnams yod pas 'byung ba'i gnod pa de dang
NK113(e)002:1445: des 'jigs la // bsam gtan bzhi pa na skyon
NK113(e)002:1446: de rnams med pas 'byung ba'i gnod pa med kyang
NK113(e)002:1447: rang rang gnas de nas 'chi 'pho bar 'gyur ba
NK113(e)002:1449: de ltar bcud 'jig pa la bar bskal bcu dgu dang /
NK113(e)002:1450: snod 'jig pa la gcig ste nyi shu'o //
NK113(e)002:1452: zhig nas stongs te bar bskal nyi shur nam mkha'
NK113(e)002:1453: gcig gi rang bzhin du gnas te rten snod dang
NK113(e)002:1454: brten pa bcud kyi 'dus byas 'dus ma byas pa'i
NK113(e)002:1455: dbyings su zhi ba ni nges pa'i don du gzugs
NK113(e)002:1456: sku chos sku'i dbyings su zhi ba'i mtshon dper gnas
NK113(e)002:1457: pa yin no // bar bskal brgyad cu po de la bskal pa chen po zhes bya'o //
NK113(e)002:1458: yang nang gi chags gnas 'jig stongs dang sbyar na /
NK113(e)002:1460: don ni 'jig dang chags pa dang //
NK113(e)002:1461: gnas pa nyid dang stongs pa dag /
NK113(e)002:1462: skye dang rga dang na dang 'chi //
NK113(e)002:1465: snga ma'i srid pa'i phung po zhig na 'chi srid
NK113(e)002:1466: kyi 'od gsal nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor lta bu ngo
NK113(e)002:1467: bo ci yang ma grub la cir yang 'char ba'i
NK113(e)002:1468: gdangs ma 'gag pa las srog gi rlung yan lag
NK113(e)002:1469: bzhi ldan g.yos nas shin tu rags pa med kyang
NK113(e)002:1470: gnas don lus kyi snang ba yad ma yud g.yo
NK113(e)002:1471: zhing 'gyur ba'i rang bzhin rlung gi dkyil 'khor ltar
NK113(e)002:1472: byung ste sred pas bcings pa las phyi ma'i gzugs
NK113(e)002:1473: phung gi nye rgyu pha ma'i khu khrag char gyi
NK113(e)002:1474: rgyun lta bu de nye bar blangs nas rlung lnga
NK113(e)002:1475: dang khyad par bsrubs byed kyi rang bzhin srid pa
NK113(e)002:1476: las kyi rlung gis yang yang bshig cing mer nur
