NK113(e)002:10062: skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig yon
NK113(e)002:10065: so so yang dag rig blo bzang //
NK113(e)002:10066: sa de legs pa'i blo gros yin //
NK113(e)002:10068: spong ba'i khyad par khams gsum gyi sgom spang chung ngu'i 'bring po zhe drug spangs /
NK113(e)002:10069: rtogs pa'i khyad par chos nyid ye shes la dbang ba'i gnas su rtogs /
NK113(e)002:10070: kun rdzob kyi yon tan stong chen 'bum phrag bcu'i rdul gyi grangs dang mnyam pa thob /
NK113(e)002:10071: shas che ba'i khyad par smon lam gyi pha rol tu phyin pa shas che /
NK113(e)002:10072: skye ba 'dzin pa'i khyad par stong gnyis kyi bdag
NK113(e)002:10073: po tshangs pa chen po'i skye ba 'dzin nus pa'o
NK113(e)002:10074: // sa bcu pa chos kyi sprin ni /
NK113(e)002:10075: ngo bo theg chen sgom lam chen po'i chen po'i
NK113(e)002:10076: skabs kyi ye shes khyad par can gang zhig yon
NK113(e)002:10079: sprin bzhin gnyis kyi nam mkha'i khams /
NK113(e)002:10080: khyab pa'i phyir na chos kyi sprin //
NK113(e)002:10082: gnyis ni gzungs dang ting nge 'dzin gyi sprin gnyis kyis rang rgyud kyi nam mkha' khyab pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10083: spong ba'i khyad par khams gsum gyi sgom spang chung ngu'i chung ngu zhe drug spangs /
NK113(e)002:10084: rtogs pa'i khyad par chos nyid phrin las la dbang ba'i gnas su rtogs //
NK113(e)002:10085: kun rdzob kyi yon tan sangs rgyas kyi zhing brjod
NK113(e)002:10086: du med pa'i yang brjod du med pa'i rdul gyi
NK113(e)002:10088: shas che ba'i khyad par ye shes kyi pha rol tu phyin pa shas che /
NK113(e)002:10089: skye ba 'dzin pa'i khyad par gnas gtsang lha'i rgyal po'i skye ba 'dzin par nus pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10090: dag sa gsum po 'dir dbang bzhi thob ste /
NK113(e)002:10091: sa brgyad pa la nyon yid gnas gyur bas rnam par mi rtog pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10092: sgo lnga gnas gyur bas zhing dag pa la dbang /
NK113(e)002:10093: sa dgu pa la rnam par rtog pa yid shes gnas gyur bas ye shes la dbang /
NK113(e)002:10094: sa bcu par yid shes kyi 'char gzhi kun gzhi'i
NK113(e)002:10095: shes pa gnas gyur pas phriin las phun sum tshogs
NK113(e)002:10096: pa la dbang 'byor te gong du rtogs pa'i khyad
NK113(e)002:10097: par bshad pa dang don gcig go //
NK113(e)002:10098: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lugs kyi sa ni /
NK113(e)002:10099: sngar gyi sa bcu po'i steng du bcu gcig kun tu 'od sprul sku'i sa dang /
NK113(e)002:10100: bcu gnyis ma chags pad+ma can longs sku'i sa dang /
NK113(e)002:10101: bcu gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'am yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa gsum mam /
NK113(e)002:10102: bcu gcig pa dpe med pa /
NK113(e)002:10103: bcu gnyis pa ye shes ldan /
NK113(e)002:10104: bcu gsum pa rdo rje 'dzin pa ste sku gsum gyi cha la btags pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10106: rdo rje snying po rgyan las /
NK113(e)002:10115: dpe dang bral ba dang shes rab 'od dang /
NK113(e)002:10117: so so'i bdag nyid dag pa'i sa ste bcu gnyis su bshad do //
NK113(e)002:10120: dbyings dang ye shes kyi cha la btags pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10121: des na 'bras bu'i sa'i rnam grangs mi 'dra ba du ma yod kyang sku gsum mam /
NK113(e)002:10122: sangs rgyas kyi yon tan la sogs pa'i ldog cha
NK113(e)002:10123: la btags pa las rgyu'i sa lam ltar gong nas
NK113(e)002:10124: gong du bgrod du med do //
NK113(e)002:10131: rtsal chen rdzogs pa la sogs pa'i tha snyad kyi rnam par dbye ba dang /
NK113(e)002:10132: rig pa chen po'i rgyud las /
NK113(e)002:10133: theg pa'i dang po bcu drug mgon //
NK113(e)002:10137: nyer thob ste re rer bzhi bzhir phye bas bcu
NK113(e)002:10138: drug tu bzhag pa la sogs pa rdo rje theg
NK113(e)002:10139: pa'i sa'i rigsa dbye rgyud sde so so nas gsungs
NK113(e)002:10141: de lta bu'i sa dang lam gang gi gnas skabs
NK113(e)002:10142: kyi spangs pa dang rtogs pa'i ye shes khyad par
NK113(e)002:10143: can rgyud la brten pa de'i ngo bo ni dam
NK113(e)002:10145: chos zhes bya ba slob pa dang mi slob pa'i
NK113(e)002:10146: gang zag rnams kyi rgyud kyi rtogs pa'i yon tan
NK113(e)002:10147: de las gzhan na rang mtshan pa zhig med pa
NK113(e)002:10148: des na'o // de ltar chos dkon mchog gi yon
NK113(e)002:10149: tan gang gis shes pa des sangs rgyas kyi bstan
NK113(e)002:10150: des na'o // pa shes shing / bstan pa shes pa des grub pa'i mtha' yang shes la /
NK113(e)002:10151: 'khor ba las gang gis skyob pa'i mtshan nyid kyang shes pa yin no //
NK113(e)002:10152: gsum pa dge 'dun gyi yon tan bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:10156: spyir dge 'dun dkon mchog gi ngo bo ni rtogs
NK113(e)002:10157: bya yang dag pa'i don ci rigs pa rig pa
NK113(e)002:10158: dang / spang bya sgrib gnyis kyi dri ma ci
NK113(e)002:10159: rigs pa las grol ba'i yon tan gnyis dang ldan
NK113(e)002:10161: de yang 'phags pa nyan thos rnams kyis ni phung
NK113(e)002:10162: sogs kyi chos rnams la rtag par 'dzin pa dang
NK113(e)002:10163: ril po gcig tu 'dzin pa'i log rtog bsal te
NK113(e)002:10164: dngos po thams cad skad cig ma dang tshogs pa
NK113(e)002:10165: tsam gyi rang bzhin du shes nas gang zag gi
NK113(e)002:10166: bdag tu 'dzin pa'i zhen yul sun phyung ba'i sgo
NK113(e)002:10167: nas nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa spangs la /
NK113(e)002:10168: rang sangs rgyas kyis de yi steng du gzung bas gdod ma nas stong par rtogs so //
NK113(e)002:10169: byang sems 'phags pa rnams kyis ni kun byang gis
NK113(e)002:10170: bsdus pa'i chos thams cad gdod ma nas spros pa
NK113(e)002:10171: thams cad dang bral ba nam mkha' lta bu'i tshul
NK113(e)002:10172: du rtogs pa na bdag 'dzin gnyis kyi zhen yul
NK113(e)002:10173: thams cad ming tsam yang med par shes nas sgrib
NK113(e)002:10174: pa gnyis po rim gyis spong bar byed pa'i mthu
NK113(e)002:10175: thogs pa med pa thob pa yin no //
NK113(e)002:10176: gnyis pa bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:10180: nyan rang gi dge 'dun la spangs rtogs kyi sgo
NK113(e)002:10181: nas dbye na zhugsa gnas gnyis re gcig tu byas
NK113(e)002:10182: te rgyun du zhugs pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10185: dgra bcom pa ste bzhi ni skyes bu zung bzhi'am /
NK113(e)002:10186: de re re la zhugs gnas gnyis re yod pa so sor phye bas ya brgyad do //
NK113(e)002:10187: de dag gi sa mtshams ni /
NK113(e)002:10188: mngon pa 'og ma ltar na mthong lam skad cig bco lnga la gnas pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10189: gong ma ltar na sbyor lam ba dang mthong lam
NK113(e)002:10190: skad cig bco lnga la gnas pa gnyis ka rgyun
NK113(e)002:10192: mthong lam skad cig ma bcu drug pa lam rjes
NK113(e)002:10193: su shes pa thob nas rgyun du zhugs pa 'bras
NK113(e)002:10194: gnas dang / rgyun zhugs des 'dod pa'i sgom spang
NK113(e)002:10195: gcig nas lnga'i bar spangs pa phyir 'ong zhugs pa
NK113(e)002:10196: gnas dang / / 'dod pa'i sgom spang drug pa spangs na phyir 'ong 'bras gnas /
NK113(e)002:10197: 'dod pa'i sgom spang bdun pa dang brgyad pa ngag rung spangs la /
NK113(e)002:10198: dgu pa ma spangs na phyir mi 'ong zhugs pa /
NK113(e)002:10199: 'dod pa'i sgom spang ril gyi spangs na phyir mi 'ong 'bras gnas so //
NK113(e)002:10200: phyir mi 'ong 'bras gnas des khams gong ma'i sgom spang spong ba la zhugs pa nas bzung /
NK113(e)002:10201: srid rtsi'i sgom spang brgyad pa spang ba'i bar 'di dgra bcom zhugs pa /
NK113(e)002:10202: khams gsum ka'i sgrib pa lhag ma ma lus par spangs pa ni dgra bcom 'bras gnas so //
NK113(e)002:10203: dgra bcom de la yang shes rab kyi cha las rnam par grol ba dang /
NK113(e)002:10204: gnyis ka'i cha las rnam par grol ba gnyis yod de /
NK113(e)002:10205: bsam gtan dang po'i nyer bsdoms mi lcogs med pa
NK113(e)002:10206: la brten nas 'jig rten las 'das pa'i lam gyis
NK113(e)002:10207: khams gsum ga'i sgrib pa ma lus pa spangs nas
NK113(e)002:10208: dgra bcom pa'i go 'phang thob kyang rnam par thar
NK113(e)002:10209: pa brgyad la snyoms par 'jug mi nus pa ni
NK113(e)002:10210: shes rab kyi cha las rnam par grol ba dang
NK113(e)002:10211: / 'jig rten dang 'jig rten las 'das pa gnyis
NK113(e)002:10212: ka'i sgo nas sgom spang spangs pas bsam gzugs sogs
NK113(e)002:10213: snyoms 'jug dgu ka la snyoms par 'jug nus pa
NK113(e)002:10214: ni gnyis ka'i cha las rnam par grol ba zhes
NK113(e)002:10215: / bya ste / 'das lam bdag med rtogs pa'i
NK113(e)002:10216: shes rab kyis nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa tsam spangs
NK113(e)002:10217: pa shes rab kyi cha las rnam grol dang /
NK113(e)002:10218: 'jig rten pa dang 'das lam gnyis ka'i sgo nas
NK113(e)002:10219: nyon mongs pa dang snyoms 'jug gi sgrib pa gnyis
NK113(e)002:10220: ka las grol ba ni gnyis ka'i cha las rnam
NK113(e)002:10221: par grol pa yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK113(e)002:10222: snyoms gajuga gi sgrib pa zhes pa ni bsam gtan
NK113(e)002:10223: gyi sems thob pa'i gegs bying rgod sogs sgrib pa
NK113(e)002:10225: zung bzhi po de dag gi nges tshig ni 'bras
NK113(e)002:10226: bu thob pa'i lam gyi rgyun la zhugs pas na
NK113(e)002:10227: rgyun zhugs / 'dod par skye ba lan gcig len pas na lan gcig phyir 'ong /
NK113(e)002:10228: de phyin chad 'dod pa'i khams 'dir mi skye bas phyir mi 'ong /
NK113(e)002:10229: nyon mongs pa'i dgra thams cad choms pas na dag bcom pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10231: 'bras bu de dag thob pa'i phyir brtson pa la zhugs pas na zhugs pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10232: de dag lam gang la gnas na mngon pa 'og
NK113(e)002:10233: ma ba rnams lam rjes shes sgom lam du bzhed
NK113(e)002:10234: cing / 'bras gnas yin na sgom lam thob pas
NK113(e)002:10235: khyab par bzhed pas rgyun zhugs phyir 'ong phyir mi
NK113(e)002:10237: dgra bcom pa mi slob ba'i lam mo //
NK113(e)002:10238: mngon pa gong ma ltar na lam rjes shes mthong lam du bzhed pas rgyun zhugs mthong lam /
NK113(e)002:10240: dgra bcom mi slob pa'i lam mo //
NK113(e)002:10241: de dag dman lam sa brgyad dang sbyar na /
NK113(e)002:10242: sbyor lam du nyan thos kyi rigs nges pa thob pa rigs kyi sa /
NK113(e)002:10243: rgyun zhugs zhugs pa ni brgyad pa'i sa ste /
NK113(e)002:10244: dgra bcom 'bras gnas nas yar lugs ldog tu bgrangs pa'i brgyad pa yin pas so //
NK113(e)002:10245: rgyun zhugs 'bras gnas ni mthong ba'i sa ste /
NK113(e)002:10246: bden bzhi'i don dang por mthong bas so //
NK113(e)002:10247: phyir 'ong 'bras gnas ni srab pa'i sa ste /
NK113(e)002:10248: 'dod nyon chung ngu gsum ma gtogs spangs pas na 'dod pa'i 'dod chags srab pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10249: phyir mi 'ong 'bras gnas ni 'dod chags dang bral ba'i sa ste /
NK113(e)002:10250: 'dod nyon dgu ka spangs pas 'dod pa'i 'dod chags dang bral ba'o //
NK113(e)002:10251: dgra bcom pa ni byas pa rtogs pa'i sa ste /
NK113(e)002:10252: rang don gyi bya ba thams cad byas zin nas
NK113(e)002:10253: zad pa dang mi skye ba shes pa'i ye shes
NK113(e)002:10254: brnyes pa'o // zad dang mi skye shes pa ni
NK113(e)002:10255: khams gsum gyi nyon mongs pa sngar yod rnams zad
NK113(e)002:10256: brnyes pa'o // pa dang / phyin chad mi skye bar shes pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10259: dgra bcom zhugs pa gsum ni nyan thos kyi sa zhes kyang bya /
NK113(e)002:10260: de'i steng du rang rgyal gyi zhugs gnas brgyad ka
NK113(e)002:10261: gcig tu brtsis nas rang sangs rgyas kyi sa zhes
NK113(e)002:10263: gnyis pa theg chen gyi dge 'dun ni /
NK113(e)002:10264: rgyal ba'i thugs kyi sras po sngar chos kyi skabs
NK113(e)002:10265: su bshad pa'i rgyu mtshan nyid kyi theg pa'i sa
NK113(e)002:10266: dang rig pa 'dzin pa'i sar gnas pa'i gang zag
NK113(e)002:10267: matha'a dag pa'i rang rang gi sa'i yon tan ji
NK113(e)002:10268: snyed yod pa thams cad ni brjod kyis mi lang
NK113(e)002:10269: yang sa bcu po so so'i yon tan sngar smos
NK113(e)002:10273: ji lta ji snyed nang gi ni //
NK113(e)002:10274: ye shes gzigs pa dag pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)002:10275: blo ldan phyir mi ldog pa'i tshogs //
NK113(e)002:10276: bla med yon tan dang ldan nyid //
NK113(e)002:10277: ces ji lta ba rig pa /
NK113(e)002:10279: nang ye shes gzigs pa'i rig pa ste gsum dang /
NK113(e)002:10280: dri med dbyings la chags med dang //
NK113(e)002:10281: thogs med phyir te dag pa yin //
NK113(e)002:10282: ye shes gzigs pa dag pas na //
NK113(e)002:10283: sangs rgyas ye shes bla med phyir //
NK113(e)002:10286: dman sgrib las grol ba gsum dang /
NK113(e)002:10287: dbye gzhi rig grol gnyis bsnan pas yon tan brgyad dang ldan par bshad la /
NK113(e)002:10288: rjes dran las legs par zhugs pa sogs bzhis bsgrub pa'i yon tan dang /
NK113(e)002:10289: thal mo sbyar ba'i 'os su gyur pa sogs kyis mchod par 'os pa'i yon tan bshad de /
NK113(e)002:10290: de rnams la ni phyi'i dge 'dun zhes bya la /
NK113(e)002:10295: las las skyes pa ste dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos
NK113(e)002:10296: skyong srung ma ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan pa
NK113(e)002:10297: rnams dang / de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la sogs
NK113(e)002:10298: pa rigs lngas bsdus pa'i 'jig rten 'das pa'i tshogs
NK113(e)002:10299: rnams dang / rnams dang / rig 'dzin bzhi'i sa la gnas pa rnams so //
NK113(e)002:10300: gnyis pa skyabs yul ngos bzung ba ni /
NK113(e)002:10301: de yang 'di ltar mya ngan las 'das pa'i go 'phang du bgrod par byed pa'i lam dang /
NK113(e)002:10302: 'khor ba las sam srid zhi gnyis kyi mtha' las
NK113(e)002:10303: skyob pa'i ngo bo ni dam pa'i chos yin te
NK113(e)002:10304: / dper na sman ma btung na sman pa ji
NK113(e)002:10305: ltar bzang yang phan mi thogs pa ltar chos de
NK113(e)002:10306: rang gis nyams su ma blang na ston pa sangs
NK113(e)002:10307: rgyas la yon tan che bas phan mi thogs te
NK113(e)002:10309: ngas ni khyod la thar ba'i lam bstan gyis /
NK113(e)002:10310: thar pa rang la rag las brtson par gyis //
NK113(e)002:10312: ji ltar bstan pa bzhin nyams su blangs na 'bras
NK113(e)002:10313: bu sangs rgyas kyang de kho na las 'byung na
NK113(e)002:10314: srid zhi'i legs tshogs gzhan lta yang ci smos te
NK113(e)002:10316: sangs rgyas kyi ston pa ni chos yin te /
NK113(e)002:10317: chos las sangs rgyas skyes pas na chos sangs rgyas
NK113(e)002:10318: kyi yum yin te sangs rgyas ni chos la gnas
NK113(e)002:10320: de lta bu'i chos de ni lha dang drang srong
NK113(e)002:10321: dge sbyor la sogs par stobs kyis ston nus pa
NK113(e)002:10322: su yang med pas na shes bya thams cad mngon
NK113(e)002:10323: sum du mkhyen cing mi 'jigs pa bzhi'i thugs mnga'
NK113(e)002:10324: ba ston pa sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das kho nas
NK113(e)002:10325: ston nus shing de lasa byung la /
NK113(e)002:10326: ston pas ji skad bstan pa'i chos de nyid tshul
NK113(e)002:10327: bzhin du rang rgyud la sgrub par byed pa la
NK113(e)002:10328: ni / rang stobs kho nas bsgrub mi nus pas
NK113(e)002:10329: rjod byed kyi lung dang brjod bya'i bslab pa nod
NK113(e)002:10330: ni / pa'i yul dang / nyams su len pa'i
NK113(e)002:10331: grogas sam bslab pa rin po che rnam pa gsum
NK113(e)002:10332: po'i mngon rtogs thams cad kyi rten gnas su gyur
NK113(e)002:10333: pa ni dge 'dun dkon mchog yin pa'i phyir /
NK113(e)002:10334: dkon mchog gsum po zhes grangs nges par thar pa
NK113(e)002:10335: don du gnyer ba rnams kyi skyabsa kyi yul du
NK113(e)002:10336: grub ste / skyabs 'gro bdun cu pa las /
NK113(e)002:10337: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun ni //
NK113(e)002:10338: thar pa 'dod pa rnams kyi skyabs //
NK113(e)002:10340: gsum pa skyabs 'gro'i dbye ba la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:10344: spyir rgyu 'bras kyi skyabs 'gro'i 'jog tshul ni 'di
NK113(e)002:10345: ltar gzhan rgyud la byon zin pa'i dkon mchog gsum
NK113(e)002:10346: la ston pa dang lam dang grogs kyi tshul gyis
NK113(e)002:10347: skyabs su 'gro ba gnas skabs rgyu'i skyabs 'gro dang
NK113(e)002:10348: / ma 'ongs pa na rang rgyud la dkon machogagasuma
NK113(e)002:10349: thob par smon pa mthar thug 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro
NK113(e)002:10350: / zhes bya / 'di dang smon sems kyi khyad par gang yin zhe na /
NK113(e)002:10351: rje btsun bsod nams rtse mos ni /
NK113(e)002:10352: smon sems la nges par dam bca' ba zhig dgos
NK113(e)002:10353: pas 'di gnyis kyi khyad par dam bca' ba'i lcags
NK113(e)002:10354: kyus rang dbang du byas ma byas kyi khyad par
NK113(e)002:10356: kun mkhyen chos kyi rgyal pos ni /
NK113(e)002:10358: 'dir don la dmigs pa'i khyad par ro zhes gsungs /
NK113(e)002:10359: de yang gzhan don bsgrub pa la rang skyabs su
NK113(e)002:10360: ma song na mi 'ong bas na gtso che bas
NK113(e)002:10362: theg chen skyabs 'gro la gzhan don du dmigs pa med par gsungs pa ma yin no //
NK113(e)002:10363: de la bstan bcos 'di nyid kyi skabs su mtshan
NK113(e)002:10364: nyid theg pa'i skyabs 'gro la rgyu'i skyabs 'gro dang
NK113(e)002:10365: / sngags kyi theg pa'i skyabs 'gro la 'bras bu'i skyab 'gro yi rnam par bzhag la /
NK113(e)002:10366: de yang skyabs su 'gro ba'i don 'dod don du
NK113(e)002:10367: gsol ba 'debs pa tsam ma yin par snying thag
NK113(e)002:10368: pa nas dam bca' ba zhig dgos pas de la
NK113(e)002:10369: gnyis las / dus gzhan grangs med gsum la sogs
NK113(e)002:10370: pa'i mthar mchog gsum rang rgyud la 'grub par 'dod
NK113(e)002:10371: nas bsgrub par dam bca' ba rgyu mtshan nyid theg
NK113(e)002:10373: de yang gnas skabs su chos dang dge 'dun gyi
NK113(e)002:10374: yon tan rim gyis rgyud la bskyed par 'dod kyang
NK113(e)002:10375: lung gi chos rtogs pa'i ye shes skyes zin pa
NK113(e)002:10376: na chu brgal zin pa'i gru ltar spang ba'i phyir
NK113(e)002:10377: dang / lam bden 'dus byas kyi cha rnams bslu zhing 'gyur ba'i chos can dang /
NK113(e)002:10378: dman lam gyis thob pa'i 'gog pa yang med pa tsam gyis phye ba yin pa'i phyir dang /
NK113(e)002:10379: dge 'dun gsum ga yang da dung spang bya ci
NK113(e)002:10380: rigs rgyud la yod pas 'jigs pa dang bcas pa'i
NK113(e)002:10381: phyir nam mchog gsum gyi yon tan mtha' dag 'dus
NK113(e)002:10382: shing tshang ba ni sangs rgyas nyag gcig yin pas
NK113(e)002:10383: mthar thug gi 'bras bu don du gnyer bya ni
NK113(e)002:10386: spang phyir bslu ba'i chos can phyir //
NK113(e)002:10387: med phyir 'jigs dang bcas pa'i phyir //
NK113(e)002:10388: chos rnams gnyis dang 'phags pa'i tshogs //
NK113(e)002:10389: gtan gyi skyabs mchog ma yin no //
NK113(e)002:10390: dam pa'i don du 'gro ba yi //
NK113(e)002:10391: skyabs ni sangs rgyas nyag gcig yin //
NK113(e)002:10392: thub pa chos kyi sku can phyir //
NK113(e)002:10393: tshogs kyang de yi mthar thug phyir //
NK113(e)002:10395: ma 'ongs pa'i dus la ltos mi dgos shing 'bras
NK113(e)002:10396: bu gzhan nas mi tshol bar da ltar mchog gsum
NK113(e)002:10397: gyi ngo bor grub zin pa rang gi semsa nyid
NK113(e)002:10398: yin pas de mngon du bya bar dam bca' ba
NK113(e)002:10399: ni 'bras bu'i skyabsa su 'gro ba'i tshul te /
NK113(e)002:10400: rdo rje'i theg pa dag gi khyad chos yin te lta ba'i dbang gis so //
NK113(e)002:10401: mdo dang sngags kyi skyabs 'gro de gnyis la'ang sngar ltar rgyu 'bras kyi skyabs 'gro gnyis re ste /
NK113(e)002:10402: dang po rgyu mtshan nyid theg pa yi skyabs yul
NK113(e)002:10403: mchog gsum tsam du ngos 'dzin pa la theg pa
NK113(e)002:10404: dman mchog gnyis po mtshungs kyang /
NK113(e)002:10407: gang zhig gsum la skyabs 'gro ba //
NK113(e)002:10408: sangs rgyas dge 'dun byed pa'i chos //
NK113(e)002:10409: mi slob pa dang gnyis ka dang //
NK113(e)002:10412: sangs rgyas dang dge 'dun gnyis de dang der byed pa'i chos mi slob pa sangs rgyas kyi dang /
NK113(e)002:10413: slob mi slob gnyis kas bsdus pa dge 'dun gyi
NK113(e)002:10414: thugs rgyud la mnga' ba'i rtogs pa'i rang bzhin lam
NK113(e)002:10416: de gnyis kyi sku ni sdug bden gyi lhag ma yin pas skyabs su mi 'gro zhing /
NK113(e)002:10417: chos dkon mchog ni de dag gi rgyud kyi dri
NK113(e)002:10418: ma spangs pa'i cha 'gog bden tsam la bshad do
NK113(e)002:10420: yul ni dkon mchog rnam pa gsuma po yang sku bzhi ye shes lnga ldan gyi sangs rgyas /
NK113(e)002:10421: lung dang rtogs pa'i bdag nyid kyi dam chos /
NK113(e)002:10422: rgyal sras sar gnas kyi 'phags pa'i dge 'dun te
NK113(e)002:10423: gsum la ston pa lam grogs kyi tshul gyi skyabs
NK113(e)002:10425: da lta lam bsgrub pas ma 'ongs pa na rang
NK113(e)002:10426: rgyud la dkon mchog gsum 'byon par smon pa 'bras
NK113(e)002:10427: bu'i skyabs 'agro'o // gsang sngagsa rdo rje theg pa'i
NK113(e)002:10428: lugs su mchog gsum de'i steng du me tog gang
NK113(e)002:10429: la phogs pa'i lha de'i gtso'i yi dam dkyil 'khor
NK113(e)002:10430: gyi gtso bo sangs rgyas dang /
NK113(e)002:10431: rgyud sde bzhi'am drug bskyed rdzogs dang bcas pa chos /
NK113(e)002:10435: gnas gsum gyi dpa' bo mkha' 'gro chos srung dang bcas pa dge 'dun yin la /
NK113(e)002:10436: de yi ngo bo bla mar 'dusa te rtsa ba'i
NK113(e)002:10437: bla ma sangs rgyas kun dngos de'i sku dge 'dun
NK113(e)002:10439: thugs sangs rgyas te dkon mchog kun 'dus su shes shing /
NK113(e)002:10440: bskyab bya dang skyob byed kyang tha dad du mi
NK113(e)002:10441: 'dzin par gnyis med kyi ngang nas skyabs su 'gro
NK113(e)002:10444: dag thob bral ba'i sems sangs rgyas //
NK113(e)002:10445: mi 'gyur dri med chos dang ni //
NK113(e)002:10446: yon tan lhun rdzogs dge 'dun nyid //
NK113(e)002:10447: yin phyir rang gi sems nyid mchog /
NK113(e)002:10448: ces pa ltar rang sems 'od gsal ba'i ye shes
NK113(e)002:10449: skyon ye zad du gnas pas dag bya dang bral
NK113(e)002:10450: zhing / yon tan ye ldan du gnas pas gsar thob dang bral ba ni sangs rgyas dang /
NK113(e)002:10451: ye nas 'gyur ba med pa'i chos nyid dri bral gyi ngo bo ni chos /
NK113(e)002:10452: yon tan dbyer med par 'dus pa ni dge 'dun
NK113(e)002:10453: te da lta nyid nas rang sems dkon mchog gsum
NK113(e)002:10454: gyi bdag nyid du shes pa ni 'bras bu'i skyabs
NK113(e)002:10455: 'agro'o // gnyis pa kun slong gi dbye ba ni
NK113(e)002:10456: skye bu'i blo rigs gsum ste rang don nyi tshe
NK113(e)002:10457: ba ste tha shal bsgrub 'dod pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10458: rang don mchog bsgrub par 'dod pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10459: gzhan don bsgrub par 'dod pa bla na med pa yi kun slong ste rnam pa gsum las /
NK113(e)002:10460: dang po ni blo gros dman pas skyes bu chung ngu zhes bya ste /
NK113(e)002:10461: de la 'ga' zhig ni grub mtha' ngan pas blo
NK113(e)002:10462: bsgyur nas skyabs ma yin pa la skyabs su sgro
NK113(e)002:10463: 'dogs te / dbang phyug dang khyab 'jug la sogs
NK113(e)002:10464: pa'i lha mthu bo che dag skyabs su brten pa
NK113(e)002:10465: 'dogs te / dang / la la dag grub mtha'
NK113(e)002:10466: la ma zhugs kyang gnas skabs tshe 'di'i 'jigs pa
NK113(e)002:10467: tsam gyis skrag nas dkon mchog gi yon tan mi
NK113(e)002:10468: shes par 'jig rten ba'i lha gzhi bdag sogs la
NK113(e)002:10469: skyabs tshol yang de dag gis ni skyob mi nus
NK113(e)002:10470: 'dogs te / dang / te / mdo rgyal mtshan dam pa las /
NK113(e)002:10471: 'jigs pas skrag pa'i mi rnams ni //
NK113(e)002:10472: phal cher ri dang nags tshal dang //
NK113(e)002:10473: kun dga' ra ba mchod rten dang //
NK113(e)002:10474: ljon shing dag la skyabs su 'gro //
NK113(e)002:10475: skyabs de gtso bo ma yin zhing //
NK113(e)002:10476: skyabs de mchog gyur ma yin te //
NK113(e)002:10477: skyabs de dag la brten pa ni //
NK113(e)002:10478: sdug bsngal kun las rab mi thar //
NK113(e)002:10480: yang 'ga' zhig nang pa'i khongs su chud pas dkon
NK113(e)002:10481: mchog la dad pa nyi tshe tsam yod kyang thar
NK113(e)002:10482: lam la 'jug pa'i nus pa med pa dag ni
NK113(e)002:10483: / ston pa gnas skabs kyi lam bsgrub pa las
NK113(e)002:10484: brtsams te ji snyed cig gsungs pa tsam la brten
NK113(e)002:10485: nas phyi ma ngan 'gro gsum gyi sdug bsngal la
NK113(e)002:10486: 'jigsa nas mngon par mtho ba lha dang mi'i bde
NK113(e)002:10487: ba don du gnyer nas 'dod bya de dang de
NK113(e)002:10488: thob pa'i bar du yul mchog gsum la skyabs su
NK113(e)002:10491: gang zhig thabs ni de dag gis //
NK113(e)002:10492: 'khor ba'i bde ba tsam dag la //
NK113(e)002:10493: rang nyid don du gnyer byed pa //
NK113(e)002:10494: skyes bu de ni tha mal 'os //
NK113(e)002:10496: de dag las mchog blo gros 'bring du gyur pa
NK113(e)002:10497: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi rigs gnyis kyis
NK113(e)002:10498: srid pa mtha' dag med 'bar bar rlubs lta bur
NK113(e)002:10499: sdug bsngal gyi rang bzhin du mthong ste des 'jigsa
NK113(e)002:10500: shing sdug bsngal de las skyob pa'i nus pa mchog
NK113(e)002:10501: gsum la yod par shes nas rang nyid gcig pu
NK113(e)002:10502: thar pa mya ngan las 'das kyi go 'phang don
NK113(e)002:10503: du gnyer nas gnas skabsa ji srid 'tsho'i bar dang
NK113(e)002:10504: / mthar thug ni nyan thos dang rang rgyal dgra
NK113(e)002:10505: bcom pa'i 'bras bu thob pa'i bar du mchog gsum
NK113(e)002:10507: de skad du mdo rgyal mtshan dam pa las /
NK113(e)002:10508: gang zhig gang tshe sangs rgyas dang //
NK113(e)002:10509: chos dang dge 'dun skyabs song ste //
NK113(e)002:10510: 'phags pa yin ni bden pa bzhi //
NK113(e)002:10511: sdug bsngal sdug bsngal kun 'byung dang //
NK113(e)002:10512: sdug bsngal yang dag 'das pa dang //
NK113(e)002:10514: 'phags lam yan lag brgyad po dag /
NK113(e)002:10515: shes rab mig gis blta byed na //
NK113(e)002:10516: skyabs de dag ni gtso yin zhing //
NK113(e)002:10517: skyabs de dag ni mchog yin te //
NK113(e)002:10518: skyabs de dag la brten nas ni //
NK113(e)002:10519: sdug bsngal kun las rab tu thar //
NK113(e)002:10521: rgyu 'bras kyi theg pa pha rol tu phyin pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10522: sngags kyi chos tshad med pa la dmigs nas sangs
NK113(e)002:10523: rgyas ye shes gzhal du med pa don du gnyer
NK113(e)002:10524: bar byed pa'i gang zag la ni skyes bu chen
NK113(e)002:10526: des ni mtha' yas pa'i sems can gzhan rnams 'khor
NK113(e)002:10527: ba'i gnas su sdug bsngal rgyu 'bras kyis gzir ba
NK113(e)002:10528: mthong nas de dag sdug bsngal de las 'don pa'i
NK113(e)002:10529: don du brtson pa spangsa te rang gcig pu thar
NK113(e)002:10530: pa'i phyir zhi ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i bde
NK113(e)002:10531: ba don du gnyer ba ni shin tu tha chad
NK113(e)002:10532: cing dam pa ma yin pa'i tshul du rig nas
NK113(e)002:10533: des 'jigas te 'khor ba na gnas pa'i sems can
NK113(e)002:10534: de thams cad gcig kyang ma lus par dbugsa 'byin
NK113(e)002:10535: chen po mi gnas pa'i mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK113(e)002:10536: sa la bsgral bar bya phyir mchog gsum gyi thun
NK113(e)002:10537: mong ma yin pa'i yon tan nam mkha' ltar tshad
NK113(e)002:10538: bzung du med pa la mtshungs pa med pa'i dad
NK113(e)002:10539: pas mthar thug byang chub chen po'i go 'phang thob
NK113(e)002:10540: ba'i bar du skyabs su 'gro ba yin no //
NK113(e)002:10541: de yang khyad par nges don gyi mdo sde dang
NK113(e)002:10542: sngags kyi brjod don zab mo khong du chud pa
NK113(e)002:10543: rnams kyis ni rang gi semas kyi gshis lugs la
NK113(e)002:10544: 'khor ba'i skyon rang mtshan pa 'bral ba dang /
NK113(e)002:10545: myang 'das kyi yon tan rang mtshan pa thob pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10546: blang dor gyi sgo nas rgyu 'bras snga phyi can
NK113(e)002:10547: du 'byung ba'i kun rdzob 'dus byas pa baslu ba'i
NK113(e)002:10548: chos thams cad gdod ma nas spangsa pa ste yod
NK113(e)002:10549: ma myong ba'i chos nyid bde gshegs snying po'i rang
NK113(e)002:10550: zhal blta zhing skyong ba 'bras bu'i skyabsa gnas mthar
NK113(e)002:10551: thug tu shes nas nyams su len pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10552: bzhi pa skyabs su 'gro tshul la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:10553: tshogs zhing mngon du bya ba dang /
NK113(e)002:10560: rgyu dang 'bras bu so sor ma nges pa'i lam ste /
NK113(e)002:10561: de yang 'di ltar spyir lha ma yin gyi stod ris lha dang /
NK113(e)002:10562: smad ris dud 'gror bsdus nas lam rgyud lngar 'jog pa ltar na /
NK113(e)002:10567: dmyal ba gdung ba'i lam sogs bshad tshul mang yang /
NK113(e)002:10568: bden gnyis shing ltar gsum pa'i lam lnga po 'di
NK113(e)002:10569: dag gi don bdag gis mjal ba'i gzhung rnams nas
NK113(e)002:10570: ma mthong la bla ma rnams kyi gsung rgyun btus
NK113(e)002:10571: na / 'di ltar gnyid 'thug gi rjes su yid
NK113(e)002:10572: shes rtog med 'khrul pa'i ngor gnas don lus kyi
NK113(e)002:10573: snang ba yang yud du ma nges pa sna tshogs
NK113(e)002:10574: par 'byung ba ni rmi lam gyi lam 1mo //
NK113(e)002:10575: dge sdig gi las dang gang gi 'bras bu smin
NK113(e)002:10576: pa de'i tshe na las des bag chags bzhag pa
NK113(e)002:10577: mngon du gyur te rigs drug gi gnas mtho dman
NK113(e)002:10578: gang du skyes pa de'i gnas don lus kyi snang
NK113(e)002:10579: ba la spyod pa ni bag chags kyi lam 2mo
NK113(e)002:10580: // gang du skyes pa'i rten der 'khor bar 'phen
NK113(e)002:10581: byed kyi dge mi dge mi g.yo ba'i las du
NK113(e)002:10582: ma 'du byad pa ni lam gyi matha'i lam 3mo
NK113(e)002:10583: // // srid pa bar ma dor 'khyams pa'i tshe
NK113(e)002:10584: na ma nges pa drug la sogs pa'i sdug bsngal
NK113(e)002:10585: gyi 'khrul 'khor sna tshogs pa myong ba ni 'khrul
NK113(e)002:10587: dge sdig gi las sna tshogs pa du ma bsags
NK113(e)002:10588: pa chud mi za zhing rang rang gi 'bras bu
NK113(e)002:10589: so sor ma 'chol bar smin pa rten cing 'brel
NK113(e)002:10590: bar 'byung ba'i chos nyid bslu ba med kyang /
NK113(e)002:10591: de thams cad 'dus byas yin pa'i gnad kyis rgyu
NK113(e)002:10592: dge sdig bsags zin kyang 'bras bu so sor smin
NK113(e)002:10593: pa ma nges pa yod de /
NK113(e)002:10594: sdig pa can gyi bshags pa tshad ldan byas pa'am /
NK113(e)002:10595: gnyen po stobs ldan skyes pa lta bus de'i 'bras bu myong mi dgos pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10596: zag bcas kyi dge ba byas kyang /
NK113(e)002:10597: khong khro la sogs pas zad nas 'bras bu ji bzhin par smin pa ma nges pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10598: yang sbyin pa gtong ba sogs dge ba zag bcas
NK113(e)002:10599: mngon mtho'i rgyu bsgrub kyang 'dun pa phyin ci log
NK113(e)002:10600: pas bsgyur te gzhan la gnod pa'i gdon chen po
NK113(e)002:10601: sogs su 'gyur bar smon lam btab pas yi dwags
NK113(e)002:10602: kyi rigs kyi 'byung por skye ba lta bu rnams
NK113(e)002:10603: ni rgyu dang 'bras bu so sor ma nges pa'i
NK113(e)002:10604: lam ste lam lnga po des srid pa'i rtse mo
NK113(e)002:10605: nas mnar med pa'i bar gyi 'gro ba thams cad
NK113(e)002:10606: bsdus shing de dag gi rang bzhin las mi 'da'
NK113(e)002:10607: bar brgyud mar 'khor bas snga ma dang gnad gcig
NK113(e)002:10608: go // de ltar lam rgyud lngar 'gro ba rnams
NK113(e)002:10609: brgyud cing 'khyams pa'i dus su sangsa rgyas bcom ldan
NK113(e)002:10610: 'das rnams kyis ni chags thogs med pa'i ye shes
NK113(e)002:10611: kyis sems can gyi khamsa dang dbang po mos pa'i
NK113(e)002:10612: bye brag thams cad ji lta ba bzhin du ma
NK113(e)002:10615: khyod 'ba' zig gi ye shes kyis //
NK113(e)002:10616: shes bya mtha' dag khyab lags kyi //
NK113(e)002:10617: khyod las gzhan pa thams cad kyi //
NK113(e)002:10618: shes bya kho na lhag pa lags //
NK113(e)002:10620: de ltar mkhyen nas kyang de la dmigs med thugsa
NK113(e)002:10621: rje chen pos nye bar dgongs te su ni rgud
NK113(e)002:10623: su ni lam gyi rten dang lam dang 'bras bu
NK113(e)002:10624: la dgod snyam du rtag par 'gro ba rnams thugs
NK113(e)002:10625: rjes rjes su bzung ba las 'da' ba med de
NK113(e)002:10627: nga ni mgon med khyed rnams kyi //
NK113(e)002:10628: grogs su gyur ba zhes sgrogs shing //
NK113(e)002:10629: thugs rje chen pos 'gro ba ni //
NK113(e)002:10630: mtha' dag 'khyud pa bzhin du bzhugs //
NK113(e)002:10632: de ltar dgongs pa na gdul bya nam gdul ba'i
NK113(e)002:10633: dus la bab ba na le lo dang bsnyel ba
NK113(e)002:10634: mi mnga' bas / dus de las skad cig ma
NK113(e)002:10635: tsam yang yol ba ste phyir 'gyang ba med par
NK113(e)002:10636: thabs gang gis tshul ji ltar 'dul bar mdzad pa'i
NK113(e)002:10637: phrin las de ma thag tu 'jug ste /
NK113(e)002:10639: rgya mtsho chu srin gnas kyi rlabs //
NK113(e)002:10640: dus las yol bar 'gyur srid kyi //
NK113(e)002:10641: gdul bar bya ba'i sras rnams la //
NK113(e)002:10642: sangs rgyas dus las yol mi mnga' //
NK113(e)002:10644: yon tan rgya che ba'i ngos nas de bzhin gshegs
NK113(e)002:10645: pa'i sku'i ba spu'i khung bu gcig gi zhing khams
NK113(e)002:10647: der sems can gyi don mdzad pa la sogs pa'i
NK113(e)002:10648: yon tan kyang cha shas tsam las matha'a dag ba
NK113(e)002:10649: ni spobs pa'i gter chen grol ba sa bcu'i dbang
NK113(e)002:10650: phyug chen po rnams kyis brjod par byas na yang
NK113(e)002:10651: / mthar ma thug pa ste brjod zin pa med
NK113(e)002:10652: pa dper na nam mkha' ldang dar la bab pa
NK113(e)002:10653: zhig gis bya lam ste nam mkha'i mtha' gzhal ba'i
NK113(e)002:10654: phyir phyin na grub pa ste thug pa'i mtha' ma
NK113(e)002:10655: snyogsa par ngal zhing dub nas slar yang sa la
NK113(e)002:10657: sku gsung thugs kyi yon tan thams cad ni bsam gyis mi khyab pa smos kyang ci dgos /
NK113(e)002:10658: des na de ltar mkhyen brtse nus gsum gyi yon
NK113(e)002:10659: tan rtag tu sems can gyi khams la rgyun chags
NK113(e)002:10660: su 'brel ba'i phyir nam yang bslu ba med pa'i
NK113(e)002:10661: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad mdun du
NK113(e)002:10662: 'dug pa dang 'dra bar mngon sum du bzhugs pa'i
NK113(e)002:10664: de yang rang nyid gang la mos pa'i sangs rgyas dang yi dam gyi lha gcig gam /
NK113(e)002:10665: rang la bka' drin dang ldan pa'i bla ma de
NK113(e)002:10666: nyid skyabs gnas kun 'dus kyi ngo bor thag bcad
NK113(e)002:10668: gsol ba 'debs pa sogs byas na skyabs gnas ji
NK113(e)002:10669: snyed pa'i thugs rje dang byin rlabs thams cad der
NK113(e)002:10670: 'du ba'i tshul gyis rang rgyud la 'jug gi /
NK113(e)002:10671: sangs rgyas byang sems rnams la gang zag rgyud tha
NK113(e)002:10672: dad par bltas nas de thams cad kyi byin rlabs
NK113(e)002:10673: rang rgyud la 'jug par re na /
NK113(e)002:10674: gnas skabs pa'i 'dod don nye tshe ba tsam las /
NK113(e)002:10675: lta dgongs khyad par can gyi dngos grub gang yang mi 'byung ste /
NK113(e)002:10676: dper na skye bu skom pas gdung ba zhig gis
NK113(e)002:10677: char bab pa'i tshe wa khar snod bzed na khang
NK113(e)002:10678: steng gi chu thams cad der 'du bas gang 'dod
NK113(e)002:10679: btung rung gi / khang steng nyid du song nas
NK113(e)002:10680: len par re yang blang du mi btub pa bzhin
NK113(e)002:10681: btung rung gi / no // gnyis pa skyabs su 'gro tshul dngos ni /
NK113(e)002:10682: 'khrul ba'i gzhan dbang du gyur pa'i skabs 'di na
NK113(e)002:10683: 'khor ba'i rang bzhin rgya che la gting zab pa
NK113(e)002:10684: 'dir bum nang gi bung ba 'khor ba'am /
NK113(e)002:10685: zo chu'i khyud mo bzhin du srid pa'i rtse mo
NK113(e)002:10686: nas mnar med pa'i bar rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi
NK113(e)002:10687: 'khor lo bar ma chad par 'byung ba'i tshul gyis
NK113(e)002:10688: yang nas yang du kha brgyud de tshul min yid
NK113(e)002:10689: byed kyi rtog pa dang nyon mongs pa drag po'i
NK113(e)002:10690: dbang gis las ngan pa sna tshogs bsagsa pa'i skyon
NK113(e)002:10691: mtshang chen po can rnams ni /
NK113(e)002:10692: 'jig rten gyi che dgu 'khora los sgyur ba'i rgyal po dang /
NK113(e)002:10694: tshangs pa la sogsa pa rang nyid 'khor ba na 'khor ba /
NK113(e)002:10695: don dam pa'i bden pa ma mthong ba 'jigs pa'i g.yang sa la rgyu ba /
NK113(e)002:10696: gnas skabs tsam du'ang phan pa dang gnod pa 'dres
NK113(e)002:10697: mar sbyin pa'i rang bzhin can gyi skyabs gzhan de
NK113(e)002:10698: dag gang gis kyang skyob par mi nus shing bslu
NK113(e)002:10699: bar 'gyur ba'i tshul mthong nas ni /
NK113(e)002:10700: srid pa'i sdug bsngal shugs drag la yun ring ba 'dis 'jigas shing skrag ba dang /
NK113(e)002:10701: dkon mchog gsum ni rang nyid 'jigs pa med pa'i
NK113(e)002:10702: gnas thob nas gzhan skyob pa'i mthu dang ldan la
NK113(e)002:10703: / zang zing gi rjes su mi blta zhing thugs
NK113(e)002:10704: rje la nye ring mi mnga' ba'i tshul la yin
NK113(e)002:10705: pa ches shing dad pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10706: thog med nas drin gyi bskyangs pa'i 'gro ba rnams
NK113(e)002:10707: sdug bsngal gyi rba klong drag po'i nang du bying
NK113(e)002:10708: nas rang gi nus pas ni mi thar /
NK113(e)002:10709: mchog gsum skyabs su ni brten mi shes pas de
NK113(e)002:10710: rnams la snying rje bzod mi phod pa ste kun
NK113(e)002:10711: slong rnam pa gsum gyis kun nas bslangs te rang
NK113(e)002:10712: don yal bar dor nas gzhan sems can gyi khams
NK113(e)002:10713: su gyur to cog thams cad 'khor ba las skyob
NK113(e)002:10714: pa'i don du skyabs su 'agro'o snyam du semsa pa
NK113(e)002:10715: skyes bu chen po'i blos dkon mchog gsum gyi yon
NK113(e)002:10716: tan rjes su dran bzhin rang rgyud la bsgrub par
NK113(e)002:10717: 'dod pas tshogs zhing gi spyan sngar dngos dang yid
NK113(e)002:10718: kyi mchod pa rgya chen pos mchod cing phyag 'tshal
NK113(e)002:10719: ba dang / sdig pa bshang pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10720: gus pa 'bul ba rnams kyis sna drangs te /
NK113(e)002:10721: bdag dang sems can thams cad thal mo sbyar nas
NK113(e)002:10722: skyabs su 'gro bar dmigs te dbyangs dang ldan pas
NK113(e)002:10723: skyabsa su 'gro ba'i tshig gi rim pa gang yang
NK113(e)002:10724: rung ba dal bus tshig gi rjes su don dran
NK113(e)002:10725: bzhin lan gsum brjod par bya zhing /
NK113(e)002:10726: khyad par sngags la zhugs pa'i gang zag gis ni /
NK113(e)002:10728: dri med sems ni sangs rgyas 'gyur //
NK113(e)002:10729: chos ni dag tu yang dag gsungs //
NK113(e)002:10730: sku ni dge 'dun zhes bya ste //
NK113(e)002:10731: byang chub sems dpa'i tshogs kyi gnas //
NK113(e)002:10732: zhes gsungs pa ltar dkon mchog kun 'dus kyi ngo
NK113(e)002:10733: bo bla ma nyid tshogs zhing gi gtso bor dmigs
NK113(e)002:10734: te skyabs su 'gro ba yin la /
NK113(e)002:10735: gang ltar yang rjes la dmigs pa med pa'i shes
NK113(e)002:10736: rab khong du chud pa'i ngang la mnyam par 'jog
NK113(e)002:10737: pa ni gnas lugs don dam pa'i skyabs 'gro ste
NK113(e)002:10738: chos nyid kyis thebs pa'i 'jig rten las 'das pa'i
NK113(e)002:10739: skyabs 'gro'i rgyu ma nor ba yin no //
NK113(e)002:10740: lnga pa skyabs 'gro'i phan yin la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:10744: ji ltar na nam mkha' la steng 'og dang phyogs
NK113(e)002:10745: chas gzhal te 'di tsam mo zhes tshad bzung med
NK113(e)002:10746: pa ltar / spyir dkon mchog gsum la brten pa'i
NK113(e)002:10747: dkar po dge ba dang nag po mi dge ba'i
NK113(e)002:10748: las gang yin yang yul gnyan pas na shin tu
NK113(e)002:10749: stobs che bas de gnyis kyi 'bras bu phan yon
NK113(e)002:10750: dang nyes dmigs kyi rnam pa thob pa yang 'di
NK113(e)002:10751: tsam mo zhes pha mtha' mi dpogas te /
NK113(e)002:10753: ji ltar nam mkha' mthar thug med pa la //
NK113(e)002:10754: 'dom gyis gzhal bas tshad bzung med pa ltar //
NK113(e)002:10755: de bzhin dkon mchog gsum la brten pa yi //
NK113(e)002:10756: yon tan dang ni sdig pa'i mtha' mi dpogs //
NK113(e)002:10758: bye brag tu skyabas su song ba'i bsod nams ni tshad med de /
NK113(e)002:10759: gal te de nyid gzugsa su gyur pa'i dngos po
NK113(e)002:10760: zhig yin srid na nam mkha'i khams thams cad kyi
NK113(e)002:10761: snod byas na de nyid kyis kyang brten par nus
NK113(e)002:10762: pa ma yin zhes te der mi shong ba lta
NK113(e)002:10763: bu ste / dri ma med pa'i mdo las /
NK113(e)002:10764: skyabs su song ba'i bsod nams gang //
NK113(e)002:10765: gal te de la gzugs mchis na //
NK113(e)002:10766: nam mkha'i khams ni kun bkang na //
NK113(e)002:10767: de ni de bas lhag par 'gyur //
NK113(e)002:10770: mchog gsum la skyabs su song ba tsam nas nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i khyur 'gro la /
NK113(e)002:10771: de yang sbyir phyi nang gi mtshams 'jog tshul mang yang /
NK113(e)002:10772: sh+aan+tim pa la sogs pa 'phags yul gyi mkhas pa 'ga' zhig skyabs 'gros 'byed par grags so //
NK113(e)002:10773: so byang sngags kyi sdom pa mtha' dag de la brten nas skye zhing gnas pas rten te /
NK113(e)002:10775: sdom pa kun la yod mod kyis //
NK113(e)002:10776: skyabs su ma song ba la med //
NK113(e)002:10778: rang bzhin dang bcas pa'i sdig sgrib thams cad kyang 'dzad cing dag par 'gyur te /
NK113(e)002:10779: nyi ma'i snying pa'i mdo las /
NK113(e)002:10780: sangs rgyas skyabs su sems can su 'gro ba //
NK113(e)002:10781: bdud rnams bye bas bsad par mi nus te /
NK113(e)002:10782: tshul khrims nyams shing blo ni 'khrugs zin kyang //
NK113(e)002:10783: de ni nges par skye ba'i pha rol 'gro //
NK113(e)002:10785: mi dang mi ma yin la sogs pa'i gnod pa'i
NK113(e)002:10786: phyogs thams cad kyis kyang spong zhing de la gnod
NK113(e)002:10788: sngon rkun po zhig la dbyug pas lan gsum brdeg
NK113(e)002:10789: pa dang bstun nas brdeg pa pos dkon mchog gsum
NK113(e)002:10790: la skyabs su 'gro ba'i tshig smras pas tshig de
NK113(e)002:10791: dang brdeg pa'i zug rngu gnyis mnyam du sems la
NK113(e)002:10792: lhang gis shar te zam 'og zhig tu bsdad pa
NK113(e)002:10793: na der mi ma yin mang po 'ong bas gnod
NK113(e)002:10794: pa ma nus par bshad pa bzhin no //
NK113(e)002:10795: ngan 'gro'i g.yang du ltung ba'i rgyu yod kyang de
NK113(e)002:10796: dag pa'i stobs kyis de ru ltung ba bsrung ste
NK113(e)002:10797: / sngon lha'i bu zhig phag tu skye bar 'gyur
NK113(e)002:10798: ba mthong nas skyabs 'gro byas pas der ma skyes
NK113(e)002:10799: pas mtshon te shes par bya'o //
NK113(e)002:10800: gang du skyes pa'i tshe rabs thams cad du dkon
NK113(e)002:10801: mchog gsum gyi snang ba dang mi 'brala zhing rgyud
NK113(e)002:10802: byin gyis brlabs par 'gyur ba dang /
NK113(e)002:10803: skyabs su song bas dkon mchog gsum gyi yon tan
NK113(e)002:10804: gyi rjes su 'gro zhing srid zhi'i phun sum tshogsa
NK113(e)002:10805: pa thams cad mthong ba'i chos tshe 'di la 'ongs
NK113(e)002:10806: te / dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK113(e)002:10807: mkhas pa dag ni yon tan rjes su 'gro //
NK113(e)002:10808: de yi dbang gis don yang phun tshogs 'grub //
NK113(e)002:10810: de ltar skyabs su song ba de la brten nas
NK113(e)002:10811: dkar po'i phyogs kyi chos thams cad gong du 'phel
NK113(e)002:10812: te dmigs bcas bsod namsa kyi tshogsa rdzogsa nas /
NK113(e)002:10813: mthar thug longs spyod rdzogs pa dang sprul pa ste gzugsa kyi sku gnyis 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK113(e)002:10815: mi gang gsum la skyabs su 'gro //
NK113(e)002:10816: de yis tshogs kyang rab rdzogs shing //
NK113(e)002:10817: sangs rgyas nyid kyang 'grub pa dang //
NK113(e)002:10820: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro'i phan yon ni /
NK113(e)002:10821: 'bras bu'i ngo bo mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin gnyug
NK113(e)002:10822: ma'i sems su ngo 'phrod pa'i skyabsa 'gro don dam
NK113(e)002:10823: bslu ba med pa ni sems snang gis bsdus pa'i
NK113(e)002:10824: chos thams cad ngo bo gang du'ang ma grub pas
NK113(e)002:10826: rtsal snang ma 'gag kyang ngos bzung dang bral bas
NK113(e)002:10827: dag ma dag sogs kyi mtshan ma med pa dang
NK113(e)002:10828: / des na dgag sgrub blang dor dang bral bas
NK113(e)002:10829: smon pa med pa ste rnam par thar pa'i sgo
NK113(e)002:10830: gsum gyi rang bzhin du 'khor 'das thams cad ro
NK113(e)002:10831: mnyam par rtogs nas skyabs gnas gzhan la brten nas
NK113(e)002:10832: 'bras bu phyi dus su re zhing smon pa med
NK113(e)002:10833: de rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i dbyingsa sems
NK113(e)002:10834: kyi gnas lugsa gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pas mi phyed
NK113(e)002:10835: pa'i rdo rje 'od gsal 'dus ma byas pa'i ye
NK113(e)002:10836: shes kyi ngang du mnyam par 'jog pa yin pa'i
NK113(e)002:10837: / phyir ro // de ltar nyams su blangs pas
NK113(e)002:10838: tha snyad du blang dor gyi sgo nas lam sgrub
NK113(e)002:10839: pa thams cad la 'khor gsum du zhen pa dang
NK113(e)002:10840: bral bas ye shes kyi tshogs rdzogsa shing rang bzhin
NK113(e)002:10841: ye nas dag pa'i chos nyid glo bur gyi sgrib
NK113(e)002:10842: pas kyang dag pa'i dag pa gnyis ldan chos kyi
NK113(e)002:10844: drug pa bslab bya la lnga ste /
NK113(e)002:10849: bslab pa bsrung ba'i phan yon bshad pa'o //
NK113(e)002:10854: thun mong gi bslab bya dang /
NK113(e)002:10855: thun mong ma yin pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK113(e)002:10857: de ltar skyabs su song nas bslaba bya la tshul bzhin du slob dgos pas /
NK113(e)002:10858: de bshad pa la spyir theg pa chen po'i lam
NK113(e)002:10859: thams cad tshogs gnyis sam thabs shes zung du 'jug
NK113(e)002:10860: pa'i sgo nas nyams su len dgos pas skabs 'dir
NK113(e)002:10861: yang rgyu 'bras kyi bslab bya gnyis bstan te /
NK113(e)002:10862: de yang mdo lam kho na'i skabs su yang skyabs
NK113(e)002:10863: 'gro sogs thabs kyi cha'i bsgrub bya thams cad la
NK113(e)002:10864: zhen med kyis rgyas thebs pa zhig med na dngos
NK113(e)002:10865: por 'dzin pa las mi grol bas shes rab kyis
NK113(e)002:10866: zin pa gal che bar gsungs shing /
NK113(e)002:10867: gzhung 'dir mdo sngags kyi nyams len rnams gnad gcig
NK113(e)002:10868: tu dril nas 'chad par mdzad pas rgyu yi skyabs
NK113(e)002:10869: 'gro'i dus su'ang sngags kyi skyabs 'gro'i yul dang 'gro
NK113(e)002:10870: tshul bslab bya sogs dang ngo bo gcig pa'i sgo
NK113(e)002:10871: nas nyams su len pa zhig dgos pas de gnyis
NK113(e)002:10872: 'gal ba can du mi blta zhing /
NK113(e)002:10873: snga phyi'am 'dir sngags kyi dngos gzhi'i nyams len gyi
NK113(e)002:10874: sngon 'gror bstan pas rgyu 'bras kyi skyabs 'gro gnyis
NK113(e)002:10875: po mnyam du nyams su len dgos shing gtso che
NK113(e)002:10876: bar las dang po pa'i skabs su rgyu 'bras blang
NK113(e)002:10878: rtogs pa nar son nas blang dor med pa'i tshul la bslab par bya ba tsam las /
NK113(e)002:10879: las dang po pa'i tshe na blang dor med pa'i lta bas zin mi dgos pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10880: rtogs pa mtho bar gyur pa na blang dor gtan nas mi dgos pa min no //
NK113(e)002:10881: de ltar nges par byas nas rim pa bzhin bshad
NK113(e)002:10882: pa las dang po rgyu'i skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya ni
NK113(e)002:10883: / dgon sde'i dpon du bsko ba lta bu'i mnga' ris dang /
NK113(e)002:10884: gser dngul dar gos sogs longs spyod mang po sbyin
NK113(e)002:10885: pa'i bya dga' ni tshe gcig gi stod smad la
NK113(e)002:10886: sogs par yang g.yo zhing mi brtan la nyes dmigs
NK113(e)002:10887: che bas de'i slad du smon ci dgos kyang /
NK113(e)002:10888: srog gi phyir yang dkon mchog gsum gtong ba min
NK113(e)002:10889: te srog ni gdon mi za bar 'bral bar 'gyur
NK113(e)002:10891: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro bas ni mngon
NK113(e)002:10892: par mtho ba dang nges par legs pa'i bde ba
NK113(e)002:10893: thams cad 'phral yun kun tu 'grub pa nyid kyi
NK113(e)002:10894: phyir tha na bzhad gad kyi phyir ram /
NK113(e)002:10895: chen po srog la bab kyang mchog gsum blos mi
NK113(e)002:10896: gtong zhing rtag tu mi brjed par skyabs 'gro yi
NK113(e)002:10897: dam du bya ba ni gal che ba'i gnad dam
NK113(e)002:10898: pa yin te / mkhas pa dang grub pa'i khyu
NK113(e)002:10899: mchog dpal ldan a ti sha yang bod du byon
NK113(e)002:10900: dus skyabs 'gro kho na gsungs pa la slob ma
NK113(e)002:10901: rnams kyis khyed la skyabs 'gro pan+di ta zhes grags
NK113(e)002:10902: kyi na 'dug pas da ni chos gzhan yang gsung
NK113(e)002:10904: jo bo'i zhal nas de lta na kho bo'i ming
NK113(e)002:10905: des kyang don chen po grub po zhes thugs dgyes
NK113(e)002:10906: dgyes mdzad skad / des na skyabs 'gro ni tha
NK113(e)002:10907: mal pa'i nyams len yin pas mi dgos so snyam
NK113(e)002:10908: nas bskyed rdzogs sogs kyi chos chen po la mtho
NK113(e)002:10909: rnyab byed pa las rang rgyud la legs par brtags
NK113(e)002:10910: te mi tshe ril po 'di la skyabs 'gro rnal
NK113(e)002:10911: ma zhig rgyud la 'byung thabs thon na khe de
NK113(e)002:10912: las che ba med par gda' snyam du sems so
NK113(e)002:10913: dgyes mdzad skad / // khyad par du dkon mchog
NK113(e)002:10914: gsum po de yi ngo bo bla ma yin pas
NK113(e)002:10915: der skyabsa su song nas rang gi bla ma la
NK113(e)002:10917: dam pa gzhan rnams la'ang mi snyan pa brjod pa
NK113(e)002:10918: sogs kyang de dang phyogs mthun gyi nyes pa yin
NK113(e)002:10919: pas bshes gnyen dam pa rnams rdzun dang g.yo sgyus
NK113(e)002:10920: bslu ba dang ngan smras dang skyon brjod kyi mi
NK113(e)002:10921: snyan pa sgrog pa spang dgos so //
NK113(e)002:10922: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i bslab bya la gnyis te /
NK113(e)002:10927: gang zhig sangs rgyas skyabs 'gro ba //
NK113(e)002:10928: de ni yang dag dge bsnyen te /
NK113(e)002:10929: nam du'ang lha ni gzhan dag la //
NK113(e)002:10930: skyabs su song ba ma yin no //
NK113(e)002:10931: dam pa'i chos la skyabs 'gro ba //
NK113(e)002:10932: 'tshe zhing gnod pa'i sems dang bral //
NK113(e)002:10934: mu stegs can dang 'grogs pa min //
NK113(e)002:10935: zhes gsungs pa de bzhin du sangs rgyas dang chos
NK113(e)002:10936: dang dge 'dun la skyabsa su song nas rim pa
NK113(e)002:10937: bzhin du / spang bya gsum ste dang po gzhan
NK113(e)002:10938: skyob pa'i nus pa med par ma zad bdag nyid
NK113(e)002:10939: ni las kyi dbang gis 'khor bar dbang med du
NK113(e)002:10940: 'khyams shing 'khor ba'i lha tshangs pa dang khyab 'jug
NK113(e)002:10941: sogs la'ang phyag mi 'tshal zhing skyabs su mi 'dzin
NK113(e)002:10942: na mkha' la rgyu ba'i yi dwags mngon shes rdzu
NK113(e)002:10943: 'phrul cung zad yod pa rnams la lta ci smos
NK113(e)002:10944: bzhin du / / 'o na dpal mgon bdun cu
NK113(e)002:10945: sogs chos skyong du mi rung ngam snyam na skyabs
NK113(e)002:10946: gsum la yid ma ches pa'am /
NK113(e)002:10947: de las lhag par bltas nas blo gtod na mi
NK113(e)002:10948: rung ba yin gyi sangs rgyas kyi phrin las sgrub
NK113(e)002:10949: pa por bltas te chos ldan gyi bya ba bsgrub
NK113(e)002:10950: pa'i grogs su bsten cing mchod na nyes pa med
NK113(e)002:10951: par ma zad phan yon kyang che'o //
NK113(e)002:10952: de yang dam tshig dang ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pa
NK113(e)002:10953: rnams kyis chos skyong srung ma rnams la rgyun du
NK113(e)002:10954: mchod nas phrin las bcol na yang /
NK113(e)002:10955: rkyen ngan glo bur ba byung ba'i tshe sgrub pa
NK113(e)002:10956: po'i mi rnams g.yel bar gyur na srung ma rnams
NK113(e)002:10957: kyis phrin las bsgrub mi nus pas na lha med
NK113(e)002:10959: de'i tshe na lhag par yid ches shing snying nye
NK113(e)002:10960: ba'i gdung shugs kyis bskul na las gang yin ci
NK113(e)002:10962: gnyis pa sems can gzhan la mi 'tshe ba ste
NK113(e)002:10963: srog gcod pa la sogs pa'i gnod pa chen po
NK113(e)002:10964: spang dgos pa lta yang ci smos /
NK113(e)002:10966: mi theg pa'i khal chen po 'gel ba dang /
NK113(e)002:10967: 'gro mi nus bzhin du zhon te 'gro ba sogs
NK113(e)002:10968: mi 'os pa'i gnod pa thams cad spang bar bya'o
NK113(e)002:10969: // gsum pa mu stegsa can dngos sam dkon mchog
NK113(e)002:10970: la yid mi ches shing skur pa'i gang zag dang
NK113(e)002:10971: mi 'grogas shing nye bar mi byed cing /
NK113(e)002:10972: tha na dkon mchog la che thang du mi 'dzin pa de la'ang blo phyogs par mi byed do //
NK113(e)002:10973: gnyis pa bsgrub pa'i bslab bya ni /
NK113(e)002:10974: dkon mchog gsum gyi rten la ma gus pa spangs
NK113(e)002:10975: te dad cing gus pas dkon mchog dngos kyi 'du
NK113(e)002:10976: shes bzhag nas bsnyen bkur zhing mchod par bya ste
NK113(e)002:10977: de la'ang bsgrub bya rnam pa gsum ste dang po
NK113(e)002:10978: rgyal po'i sku gzugs bris 'bur gyi rnam pa bzo
NK113(e)002:10981: ji ltar bde gshegs sku gzugs shing las kyang //
NK113(e)002:10982: bgyis pa ci 'dra'ang rung ste mkhas pas mchod //
NK113(e)002:10983: ces pa ltar gus pas mchod par bya yi mi legs so zhes 'phya zhing smod pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10984: sri zhu lhod pa'i gnas su 'jog pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10986: btsong ste rin la spyod pa sogs brnyas thabs thams cad spang dgos te /
NK113(e)002:10988: sku gzugs rnam pa mang por der sprul nas /
NK113(e)002:10989: 'gro ba dge la spyod pa'i don byed do //
NK113(e)002:10990: zhes bzo sprul pa'i rang bzhin yin pa'i phyir ro //
NK113(e)002:10991: gnyis pa rang gzhan gyi rgyud kyi bslab pa gsum
NK113(e)002:10992: dang lung gi chos thams cad la gus par bya
NK113(e)002:10993: zhing lung gi chos kyi rten yi ge'ang zong du
NK113(e)002:10994: 'tshong ba dang / gta' mar 'jog pa dang /
NK113(e)002:10997: 'bru thog tu so dreg skud pa sogs spangs nas gus pa bya dgos te /
NK113(e)002:10999: lnga brgya'i tha mar gyur pa na //
NK113(e)002:11000: nga ni yi ge'i zugs su gnas //
NK113(e)002:11001: nga yin snyam du yid byos la //
NK113(e)002:11002: de tshe de la gus par gyis //
NK113(e)002:11004: de bzhin du gsum pa yang /
NK113(e)002:11005: rab byung gi dge 'dun nam rtags tsam 'dzin pa
NK113(e)002:11006: yan chad la gus shing bsnyen bkur byed dgos kyi
NK113(e)002:11007: brnyas pa dang ngan smras dang ming 'dogs sogs mi
NK113(e)002:11008: bya ste skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya gtong bar ma zad
NK113(e)002:11009: dge 'dun la brnyas pa'i nyes pa'ang tshabs che ste
NK113(e)002:11010: / sngon shed bu ser skyas slob pa dang mi
NK113(e)002:11011: slob pa'i dge 'dun rnams la glang po'i mgo can
NK113(e)002:11012: sogs smras pas chu srin nya'i rigs can mgo brnyan
NK113(e)002:11013: mi 'dra ba bco brgyad yod par skyes nas yun
NK113(e)002:11014: ring por sdug bsngal ba'i tshul lung rnam 'byed las
NK113(e)002:11016: der ma zad tha na tshul khrims 'chal ba rtags
NK113(e)002:11017: dang ma bral ba yin yang khyu mchog shi ba'i
NK113(e)002:11019: gla ba'i ro la rtsi ma gi ta yod pa ltar /
NK113(e)002:11020: sngon legs par spyad pa'i 'bras bu cung zad dang
NK113(e)002:11021: ldan pa yin pas ma 'ongs pa na theg gsum
NK113(e)002:11022: gang rung gi phyir mi ldog pa thob pa'i chos
NK113(e)002:11023: can yin pa'i phyir gzhan las 'phags te /
NK113(e)002:11024: ji ltar na bdag cag gi ston pas sngon smon lam btab pa'i dbang gis te /
NK113(e)002:11025: snying rje pad+ma dkar po las /
NK113(e)002:11026: sems can gang dag bdag gi bstan pa la chos
NK113(e)002:11027: gos ngur smrig bgos par gyur pa las ltung ba'i
NK113(e)002:11028: rtsa ba byung bar gyur pa'am /
NK113(e)002:11029: nyon mongs pa can gyi lta ba la zhugs par gyur pa'am /
NK113(e)002:11030: dkon mchog gsum la 'khrul bar gyur cing /
NK113(e)002:11031: nongs pa dang bcas pa'i dge slong dang dge slong
NK113(e)002:11032: ma dang dge bsnyen dang dge bsnyen ma gang dag
NK113(e)002:11033: skad cig tsam bdag la ston pa'i 'du shes sam
NK113(e)002:11034: / gus pa'i sems bskyed par gyur pa'i sems can
NK113(e)002:11035: de dag las btsun pa bcom ldan 'das gal te
NK113(e)002:11036: bdag gis tha na sems can 'ga' tsam zhig spangs
NK113(e)002:11037: shing theg pa gsum po dag gis phyir mi ldog
NK113(e)002:11038: par lung bstan par ma gyur na bdag mngon par
NK113(e)002:11039: rdzogs par 'tshang rgya bar ma gyur cig /
NK113(e)002:11041: sa'i snying po 'khor lo bcu pa'i mdo las /
NK113(e)002:11042: tsam pa ka yi me tog rnyis gyur kyang //
NK113(e)002:11043: me tog rnam pa gzhan las shin tu lhag /
NK113(e)002:11044: dge slong tshul khrims nyams shing sdig spyod kyang //
NK113(e)002:11045: mu stegs can dag thams cad kun las 'phags //
NK113(e)002:11047: des na de nyid khyad du bsad nas brnyas thabs
NK113(e)002:11048: byed pa yang nyes pa shin tu che bar bshad
NK113(e)002:11050: rigs kyi bu de ltar tshul khrims nyams pa sdig
NK113(e)002:11051: pa spyod pa'i dge slong dag de ltar chos las
NK113(e)002:11052: 'gal ba'i sdig pa chen po byas mod kyi /
NK113(e)002:11053: 'on kyang de bstan pa la gnas shing skra dang
NK113(e)002:11054: kha spu bregs te gos ngur smrig bgos nas spyod
NK113(e)002:11055: lam dang cha lugs 'phags pa rnams dang mthun te
NK113(e)002:11058: khyim pa rnams kyis khyim pa'i chos nyid dang yang sbyar du mi gnang na /
NK113(e)002:11064: lus kyi yan lag gtubs pa dang /
NK113(e)002:11065: 'tsho ba'i dbang po dang bral na chos ma yin pa byed pa lta ci smos /
NK113(e)002:11068: khyim pa rnams kyi gal te de ltar bya na
NK113(e)002:11069: kha na ma tho ba'i sdig pa chen po thob
NK113(e)002:11070: par 'gyur te gdon mi za bar mtshams med pa'i
NK113(e)002:11073: des na bdag cag ston pa thugs rje can gyi
NK113(e)002:11074: bstan pa'i lhag zhabs su skyes nas mchog gsum gyi
NK113(e)002:11075: rten dang ngur smrig gi rtags 'chang ba'i dge 'dun
NK113(e)002:11076: gyi tshogs pa tsam mjal du yod pa 'di yang
NK113(e)002:11077: stes dbang gis ma yin te /
NK113(e)002:11078: ston pa de'i bka' drin las byung ba yin pas
NK113(e)002:11079: de la drin gzo ba'i phyir du yang yul de
NK113(e)002:11080: rnams la / rang gi sgo gsum longs spyod dang bcas pas bsnyen bkur byed pa dang /
NK113(e)002:11081: rgyu mtshan de lta bu mi shes shing dad pa'i
NK113(e)002:11082: zhing la bsod nams kyi sa bon 'debs mi nus
NK113(e)002:11083: pa rnams la yang lhag pa'i bsam pas tshul de
NK113(e)002:11084: lta bu la sbyar na bsod nams lhag par che
NK113(e)002:11085: bar bshad pas gzhan la bskul ma gdab pa dang
NK113(e)002:11086: / nyin dang mtshan mo'i dus thams cad du'am /
NK113(e)002:11089: tha na nyin mtshan gyi cha re rer dkon mchog
NK113(e)002:11090: gsum gyi yon tan brjed pa spangsa nas rjes su
NK113(e)002:11091: dran bzhin rang skyabsa su 'gro zhing gzhan yang de
NK113(e)002:11092: la 'god par byas na da lta blo gang la
NK113(e)002:11093: goms pa de 'chi ba'i tshe na'ang 'byung bas nyams
NK113(e)002:11094: len gzhan med kyang 'chi ba'i tshe sangs rgyas rjes
NK113(e)002:11095: su dran pa zhig byung na don che ste /
NK113(e)002:11097: lus dang ngag dang yid rab dang ba yis //
NK113(e)002:11098: rtag tu sangs rgyas dag gi basngagasa pa brjod //
NK113(e)002:11099: de ltar des ni sems kyi rgyud bsgoms pas //
NK113(e)002:11100: nyin mtshan du yang 'jig rten mgon po mthong //
NK113(e)002:11101: nam zhig de ni na zhing mi bde nas //
NK113(e)002:11102: shi la thug pa'i sdug bsngal tshor byung na //
NK113(e)002:11103: sangs rgyas la ni dran pa mi nyams te //
NK113(e)002:11104: sdug bsngal tshor bas 'phrog par yongs mi nus //
NK113(e)002:11106: gnyis pa 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro'i bslab bya ni /
NK113(e)002:11107: gong du ji skad bshad pa ltar dkon mchog gi
NK113(e)002:11108: rang bzhin rgyud gzhan gyis bsdus pa ma yin pa'i
NK113(e)002:11109: don rtogs pa'i 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro de yi bslab
NK113(e)002:11110: bya ni sems kyi chos nyid thub pa chos kyi
NK113(e)002:11111: sku'i ngo bo yin pas sems dang sems byung nyi
NK113(e)002:11112: ma dang 'od zer bzhin du mtshungs par 'jug pa'i
NK113(e)002:11113: rtsal snang thams cad bral thob spangsa pa'i dbyingsa la
NK113(e)002:11114: thim ste spros pa nye bar zhi ba'i tshe byang
NK113(e)002:11115: chub pa yin pas mchog gsum la skyob byed dang
NK113(e)002:11116: bdag la bskyab byar mi 'dzin cing /
NK113(e)002:11117: cho ga'i sgo nas blangs ba la sogs pa'i tha
NK113(e)002:11118: snyad las 'das pa'i phyir gtong rgyu zhes pa'ang btagsa
NK113(e)002:11119: pa'i tshig bla dwags tsam du zad pa yin pa'i
NK113(e)002:11120: phyir / da lta nas rtsal snang gang la'ang bdag
NK113(e)002:11121: dang bdag gir mi zhen par thams cad chos skur
NK113(e)002:11122: lhongs pa 'i thabs la mkhas par ma byas na
NK113(e)002:11123: sems kyi rang bzhin de ltar yin pa tsam dang
NK113(e)002:11124: go yul tsam du ngo 'phrod pas gar yang mi
NK113(e)002:11125: phyir / phyin te / rgyal po la gdams pa las /
NK113(e)002:11126: rnam rtog bdag tu 'dzin pa'i dgra chen po //
NK113(e)002:11127: 'di ni rgyu bzhin dngos po med bzhin du //
NK113(e)002:11128: thog ma med nas bdag la gnas nas ni //
NK113(e)002:11129: bdag gi chos sku yid bzhin rin chen de //
NK113(e)002:11130: gzod ma'i mu nas dgra yis brkus nas su //
NK113(e)002:11131: mtshan ma'i tshang tshing gseb tu sbas nas bdag /
NK113(e)002:11134: gnyis pa skyabs 'gro'i gtong mtshams ni /
NK113(e)002:11135: rgyu yi skyabs 'gro gtong ba'i mtshamsa skyob byed dang
NK113(e)002:11136: bskyab byar bzung nas yul mchog gsum la skyabs su
NK113(e)002:11137: 'gro bar dam bca' ba ni skyabs 'gro mtshan nyid
NK113(e)002:11138: pa ste de dang mi mthun pa'i blo sangs rgyas
NK113(e)002:11140: las 'bras med do snyam pa sogs skyabs su 'gro
NK113(e)002:11141: ba'i yul dkon mchog gsum la log lta skyes te
NK113(e)002:11142: spangs pa dang / bsgrub par ma nus nas skyabs 'gro'i bslab pa phul bas gtong la /
NK113(e)002:11143: gal te dkon mchog blos ma btang yang phyi rol
NK113(e)002:11144: pa'i ston pa dang bstan pa la go bsdur nas
NK113(e)002:11146: cung zad tsam las khyad par med snyam pa ni
NK113(e)002:11147: gtong ba la phyogs nye ba yin pas phyi rol
NK113(e)002:11150: gzhung lugs sogs kyi yon tan ji tsam thos shing
NK113(e)002:11151: mthong yang brtags na skyon gyi rang bzhin las ma
NK113(e)002:11152: 'das pas dkon mchog gsum gyi che ba'i yon tan
NK113(e)002:11153: gyi phyogs tsam du'ang mi 'gro ba'i tshul la nges
NK113(e)002:11154: shes gting nas rnyed de blo sna gtan nas bsgyur
NK113(e)002:11155: mi btub pa zhig dgos so //
NK113(e)002:11156: de ltar yang khyad par 'phags bstod las /
NK113(e)002:11157: mu stegs can gyi gzhung lugs la //
NK113(e)002:11158: ji lta ji ltar rnam bsam pa //
NK113(e)002:11159: de ltar de ltar mgon khyod la //
NK113(e)002:11160: bdag gi sems ni dad par gyur //
NK113(e)002:11162: bdag ni ston pa gzhan spangs nas //
NK113(e)002:11163: khyod la skyabs su mchi lags kyis //
NK113(e)002:11164: de ci'i slad du zhe na khyod //
NK113(e)002:11165: skyon mi mnga' la yon tan ldan //
NK113(e)002:11167: de las gzhan spang sgrub kyi bslab bya rnams las
NK113(e)002:11168: gang yang rung ba nyamsa na skyabs 'gro rtsa ba
NK113(e)002:11170: de'i nyes pas rgyud dman par 'gyur zhing ngan song du ltung ba'i las sogs par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK113(e)002:11171: dper na lus thams cad rma yis gang ba'i gang
NK113(e)002:11172: zag gis shin tu bag byed pa bzhin dran shes
NK113(e)002:11173: bag yod kyi sems bsgrimsa te bslab bya phra mo
NK113(e)002:11174: tsam yang ma nyams par bsrung bar bya'o //
NK113(e)002:11175: gsum pa gtong ba'i rgyu ni /
NK113(e)002:11176: sngon yang dkon mchog gsum la yid ma ches te
NK113(e)002:11177: 'jig rten pa'i lha la skyabs su brten pa dang
NK113(e)002:11178: / rmongs pa'i las thabs sna tshogs bgyis pa'i lasa
NK113(e)002:11179: kyi rgyu mthun da lta yang steng du slebs nas
NK113(e)002:11180: ce spyang gdug pa'i sems bzhin bsod nams zad pa'i
NK113(e)002:11181: mi la bsam ngan skye ba chos nyid yin pas
NK113(e)002:11182: phyin ci log gi rtog pa ngan pas skabsa btsal
NK113(e)002:11183: zhing rgyud gang ba rnams kyis 'jig rten na grags
NK113(e)002:11184: pa'i dbang gis tshig tsam du dkon mchog gi mtshan
NK113(e)002:11185: dang skyabs 'gro gsol 'debs sogs sgrog par byed na'ang
NK113(e)002:11186: don ni de dang 'dzol ba'i phyir dkon mchog gsum
NK113(e)002:11187: la blo gcig tu mi khel bar yid gnyis te
NK113(e)002:11188: skyob bam mi skyob snyam pa'i blo rtse gnyis su
NK113(e)002:11189: gyur pa de la ni mchog gsum gyi thugs rje
NK113(e)002:11190: dang byin rlabs gang yang mi 'jug pas snod ngan
NK113(e)002:11191: pa ste de'i sems rgyud du dkon mchog gsum gyis
NK113(e)002:11192: 'phral yun kun tu bslu ba med cing skyob nges
NK113(e)002:11193: pa'i tshul la nges shes kyi dad pa bri ba
NK113(e)002:11194: dang med pa'i rtagsa su 'jig rten na lha dang
NK113(e)002:11195: gzhi bdag sogs kyi ming btags kyang don du mkhas
NK113(e)002:11196: la rgyu ba'i yi dwagsa las kyis rdzu 'phrul dang
NK113(e)002:11197: mngon shes cung zad thob pa rnams la brten cing
NK113(e)002:11198: chos dang 'gal ba'i sdig las kyi mchod pa dang
NK113(e)002:11199: bstod pa sogs byas nas blo gtod pa dang /
NK113(e)002:11200: 'jig rten pa'i lugs kyi mnga' thang cung zad yod
NK113(e)002:11201: pa'i rgyal po dang blon po dang sdig pa'i grogs
NK113(e)002:11202: po sogs la blo gtan 'cha' bar byed kyang /
NK113(e)002:11203: de dag gis 'phral du gnod pa phran bu tsam las skyob ba dang /
NK113(e)002:11204: zang zing sogs kyi sgo nas phan cung zad re
NK113(e)002:11205: btags pa ltar snang yang de dag la ci tsam
NK113(e)002:11206: brten pa de tsam gyis chos min log pa'i lam
NK113(e)002:11207: la sbyar bas tshe 'di nyid la'ang kha rje dbang
NK113(e)002:11208: thang thams cad nyamsa te mthar gri kha dang mtshon
NK113(e)002:11209: khar 'achi'am / ltogs gri dang 'khyags grir 'chi ba
NK113(e)002:11210: sogs shin tu mang ba mthong chos su yod la
NK113(e)002:11211: khar 'achi'am / / phyi mar yang ngan song du 'gro ste /
NK113(e)002:11212: tshangs pas byin gyis zhugs pa las /
NK113(e)002:11213: sangs rgyas som nyi za ba g.yang sa'i mchog /'jig rten kun gyis skyabs byed mi nus te /
NK113(e)002:11214: blo chung de ni bstan las nyams gyur pas //
NK113(e)002:11215: mgon med de ni ngan 'gror 'gro bar 'gyur //
NK113(e)002:11217: gal te de 'dra ba'i skyabs dman pa bsten pa dang /
NK113(e)002:11218: chos ma yin pa'i lam tshabs po che bsags pa
NK113(e)002:11219: de rnams la tshe 'dir dkon mchog gi bka' chad
NK113(e)002:11220: mi 'byung zhing tshe ring zhing longs spyod dang ldan
NK113(e)002:11221: la nad sogs med pas bde bar 'tsho ba dag
NK113(e)002:11222: snang yang / de ni sngon gyi dge 'bras cung
NK113(e)002:11223: zad re yod pa tshe 'dir mnyam du smin te
NK113(e)002:11224: de tsam gyis longs spyad zin nas phyi ma ngan
NK113(e)002:11225: song du lhung nas thar pa'i dus skabs shin tu
NK113(e)002:11226: dka' ba'i snga ltas yin la /
NK113(e)002:11227: yang 'ga' zhig dkon mchog la blo gtad nas chos
NK113(e)002:11228: bzhin bsgrubs kyang tshe 'dir longs spyod dbul zhing nad
NK113(e)002:11229: mang ba sogs mi 'dod pa du ma 'byung ba
NK113(e)002:11230: lta bu yod kyang de ni dkon mchog gi thugs
NK113(e)002:11231: rje dang chos kyi byin rlabs kyis sngon bsags kyi
NK113(e)002:11232: lam ngan thams cad tshe 'dir mi 'dod pa dang
NK113(e)002:11233: sdug bsngal cung zad myong ba de tsam gyis zad
NK113(e)002:11234: de phyi ma phan chad skyid kyi mgo zin pa
NK113(e)002:11235: yin pas blo gros dang ldan zhing las 'bras la
NK113(e)002:11236: yid ches pa'i gang zag rnams la ni de dag
NK113(e)002:11237: dad pa'i rgyur 'gro ba las the tshom mi skye
NK113(e)002:11238: yang / blo dman chos kyi skal ba med pa
NK113(e)002:11239: dag gis ni tshul de la dpag nas las 'bras
NK113(e)002:11240: mi bden no mi dge ba ci byas kyang mi
NK113(e)002:11241: rung ba med do snyam du bltas nas sdig pa'i
NK113(e)002:11242: 'bras bu smin par ma gyur pa de srid du
NK113(e)002:11243: de'i nyes pa mi mthong ste /
NK113(e)002:11244: ched du brjod pa'i tshoms las /
NK113(e)002:11245: ji srid sdig pa ma smin pa //
NK113(e)002:11246: de srid sdig pa rung bar blta //
NK113(e)002:11247: gang tshe sdig pa smin gyur pa //
NK113(e)002:11248: de tshe sdig pa mthong bar 'gyur //
NK113(e)002:11250: des na dkon mchog gsum gyi snang ba yod pa'i
NK113(e)002:11251: sar skyes kyang de'i yon tan mi mthong ba'i dmus
NK113(e)002:11252: long lta bur gyur pa'i skal chad rnams la dkon
NK113(e)002:11253: mchog gi thugs rje dang byin rlabs 'jug pa'i go
NK113(e)002:11254: skabs med kyang / skal ba dang ldan pa rnams
NK113(e)002:11255: kyi ni mchog gsum gyi thugs rje'i nyi ma'i 'od
NK113(e)002:11256: snang la brten nas 'di dang phyi ma'i legs dgu'i
NK113(e)002:11257: don thams cad bsgrub pa'i bya ba byed de /
NK113(e)002:11258: dkon mchog t+wa la'i mdo las /
NK113(e)002:11259: ji ltar dmus long nyid ma mi mthong yang //
NK113(e)002:11260: de med ma yin 'jig rten kun la 'char //
NK113(e)002:11261: mig dang ldan pas snang ba shes gyur nas //
NK113(e)002:11262: kun kyang so sor rang gi las la 'jug /
NK113(e)002:11263: zhes pa la sogs pa ltar ro //
NK113(e)002:11264: bzhi pa de'i gnyen po ni /
NK113(e)002:11265: 'jig rten 'di na rtag tu gnas par rlom pa'i
NK113(e)002:11266: sa gzhi dang nam mkha' ri rab dang gling bzhi
NK113(e)002:11267: la sogs pa'i bkod pa 'di dag rnams kyang da
NK113(e)002:11268: lta yan man du gnas pa'i go sa 'di nyid
NK113(e)002:11269: ma 'ongs pa na snod kyi 'jig rten zhig ste
NK113(e)002:11270: thams cad stongs par 'gyur bas sa gzhi dang ri
NK113(e)002:11271: rab sra 'thas kyi rnam par snang ba 'di dag
NK113(e)002:11272: gi gnas su nam mkha' kho na 'ong la /
NK113(e)002:11273: yang chags pa'i 'go brtsams pa nas rlung gi dkyil
NK113(e)002:11274: 'khor gyis nam mkha'i gnas su sa gzhi sogs brten
NK113(e)002:11276: gza' skar gyi rten gzhi go la'i rlung gi 'khrul
NK113(e)002:11277: 'khor zhig pas nyi zla yang so na mi gnas
NK113(e)002:11278: pas thang du lhung ba'i tha snyad grub pa'am /
NK113(e)002:11279: rtag tu nam mkhar rgyu ba'i nyi zla'i gzhal med
NK113(e)002:11280: khang la brten pa'i lha'i bu dag kyang sa'i steng
NK113(e)002:11281: dang 'og gi 'phro ba rnams kyi gnas su lhung
NK113(e)002:11282: ba srid kyang / dkon mchog gsum skyabs gnas su
NK113(e)002:11283: dam bcas te rgyal ba'i bka' bzhin bsgrub na mchog
NK113(e)002:11284: gsum gyi thugs rje dang de bzhin gshegs pa'i bden
NK113(e)002:11285: pa'i gsung gis ni nam yang bslu ba mi srid
NK113(e)002:11286: pa'i tshul 'phags pa rnams la mngon sum yin pas
NK113(e)002:11287: rtag tu dkon mchog las blo 'gyur mi srid kyang
NK113(e)002:11288: ba srid kyang / / da lta las dang po
NK113(e)002:11289: pa'i dus na rjes su dpag pa'i sgo nas nges
NK113(e)002:11290: shes nang nas 'khrungs te rkyen cis kyang blo mi
NK113(e)002:11291: 'gyur zhing shin tu brtan pa zhig ni rnam pa
NK113(e)002:11292: kun tu 'phral yun gyi don chen po yod pa
NK113(e)002:11296: sa gzhi nam mkhar 'gyur yang srid //
NK113(e)002:11297: de bzhin gshegs pas gsungs pa la //
NK113(e)002:11298: gzhan du 'gyur ba ma mchis so //
NK113(e)002:11300: lnga pa bslab pa bsrung ba'i phan yon bshad pa ni /
NK113(e)002:11301: de ltar skyab su song nas skyid sdug legs nyes
NK113(e)002:11302: gang gi tshe na'ang dkon mchog gsum gyi thugs rje
NK113(e)002:11303: dang byin rlabs kyi yon tan mi brjed par dran
NK113(e)002:11304: bzhin bslab pa tshul bzhin bsrung ba'i phan yon ni
NK113(e)002:11305: / rmi lam na yang chur lhung ba dang dgra
NK113(e)002:11306: dang gcan gzan gyis ded pa sogs snang na de
NK113(e)002:11307: ma thag dkon mchog gsum mthong ba'am /
NK113(e)002:11308: dran nas gsol ba btab pa tsam gyi 'jigs pa de dag zhi ba dang /
NK113(e)002:11309: mi dge ba'i rtog pa ngan pa zhig skyes na'ang
NK113(e)002:11310: rgyal ba sras bcas kyi thugs kyis khrel ba dang
NK113(e)002:11311: dam pa'i chos dang 'gal bar shes nas de la
NK113(e)002:11312: gzob pa'i bag yod pa dran zhing de'i sbyor ba
NK113(e)002:11314: tshul khrims dag cing ting 'dzin brtan la shes rab
NK113(e)002:11315: gsal ba la sogs pa'i yon tan kun gyis tshe
NK113(e)002:11317: skye ba gzhan tshe rabas sngon ma rnams su dkon
NK113(e)002:11318: mchog la dad pa la sogs pa'i yon tan drana
NK113(e)002:11319: zhing de'i rgyu mthun dad pa dang skyabs su 'gro
NK113(e)002:11320: ba la sogs pa'i dge ba'i tshogs spel ba la
NK113(e)002:11321: dga' ba dang / bar do'i gnas na'ang sangs rgyas dang byang sems rnams kyi zhal mthong ba'am /
NK113(e)002:11322: de dag gi yon tan rjes su dran nas dad
NK113(e)002:11323: pa la sogs pa'i stobs kyis 'khrul snang dang 'jigs
NK113(e)002:11324: skrag thams cad rang sar zhi nas dag pa'i zhing
NK113(e)002:11325: dang mtho ris kyi gnas su bgrod par sla ba
NK113(e)002:11326: dang / mthar thug sa lam gyi yon tan thams
NK113(e)002:11327: cad mthar phyin te mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas
NK113(e)002:11328: nas dkon mchog gsum gyi ngo bor bzhugs te lus
NK113(e)002:11329: can ma lus pa kun gyi nyes pa'i tshogs thams
NK113(e)002:11330: cad 'joms pa'i dpung mngon par mtho ba dang nges
NK113(e)002:11331: par legs pa'i go 'phang la 'god pa'i phan pa
NK113(e)002:11332: nye bar bsgrub pa'i gnyen mchog gi bdag nyid du
NK113(e)002:11333: dang / 'gyur ro // yon tan rin po che'i mdzod dga' ba'i char zhes bya ba las /
